ORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\"><img style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"conimg\" alt=\"知悉你的明眸，告别眼睛干痒Qm.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130916/f97074ce757bc3589f056f0e5eff83de.jpg\" /></td></tr><tr style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 14px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\"><td style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\"><div style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" align=\"center\">蛋黄焗南瓜</div></td><td style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\"><div style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" align=\"center\">凉拌西兰花</div></td><td style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\"><div style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" align=\"center\">熘肝尖</div></td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; POSITION: relative; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 10px; WIDOWS: 2; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 20px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 20px; FONT: 14px/24px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; ORPHANS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 10px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　六、眼睛疾病影响</p><p style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; POSITION: relative; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 10px; WIDOWS: 2; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 20px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 20px; FONT: 14px/24px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; ORPHANS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 10px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　正常情况下结膜、角膜表面覆盖有由睑板腺分泌的油脂层，其下为泪腺分泌的水样液层，最内层为杯状细胞分泌的粘液层。这三层共同形成一层保护及湿润结膜的泪膜，当结膜上皮细胞层和结膜下组织因病变而被破坏，如严重沙眼瘢痕、白喉性结膜炎、结膜天疱疮、结膜化学伤或热烧伤、X线照射后，由于广泛瘢痕形成，使泪腺导管被瘢痕所阻，副泪腺及结膜杯状细胞被破坏，以致泪液和粘液不能湿润眼球。此外，各种原因所造成的眼睑闭合不全，使结膜和角膜长期暴露而引发 干眼病。</p><table style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; WIDOWS: 2; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px auto; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; BORDER-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BORDER-COLLAPSE: collapse; FONT: 14px/24px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; ORPHANS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"500\" align=\"center\"><tbody style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 14px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\"><tr style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 14px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\"><td style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: center; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\"><img style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"conimg\" alt=\"知悉你的明眸，告别眼睛干痒Cy.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130916/8e0119bc4013337c0e0ac056d4949348.jpg\" /></td><td style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\"><img style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"conimg\" alt=\"知悉你的明眸，告别眼睛干痒Cr.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130916/3331e66a8e1a0a6f6f5effba6d0ba545.jpg\" /></td><td style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\"><img style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"conimg\" alt=\"知悉你的明眸，告别眼睛干痒Qm.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130916/c4ab4deec1aa27491695035f62420fcc.jpg\" /></td></tr><tr style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 14px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\"><td style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\"><div style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" align=\"center\">橙汁冬瓜</div></td><td style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\"><div style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" align=\"center\">雪梨菊花粥</div></td><td style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\"><div style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" align=\"center\">苹果玉米羹</div></td></tr></tbody></table>', '', '', '1379863896', '122', '1', '', '', '', '3', '周边小编', '1');
INSERT INTO `articles` VALUES ('25', '中秋国庆通吃，小意思', '', '<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">刚刚过完中秋节，紧接着就是接踵而来的国庆大长假，在假期里应该都是亲戚、朋友聚会的好时机，期间，就总是会不可避免的吃吃喝喝!所以，这个时候也是最容易悄悄长肉的时候，南宁周边网小编在此提醒大家，爱美食的同时可别忘了刮油哦。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　保持身材的苗条需要注重科学的饮食，做到荤素搭配，才能吃的更好更健康。餐桌上增加“刮油食物”，但并不是一下子全改吃素食，那样极易导引起胃不适，也容易导致营养失衡。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative; text-align: center;\"><img class=\"conimg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130923/52bd4d33f83792c4f27a7d7362578b2f.jpg\" alt=\"文章内首图500.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"428\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: block; max-width: 550px;\" /></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　1、 竹笋</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　竹笋含有丰富的膳食纤维，是名符其实的“体内垃圾清除器”，俗话讲：“吃一餐笋，能刮三天的油”，但需要注意的是，竹笋中含草酸较多，食用前应先用开水焯过。而且所含的草酸，会影响人体对钙的吸收，所以儿童不宜多食。</p><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"500\" align=\"center\" border=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 24px;\"><tbody style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; text-align: center;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"秒杀双节，吃货毫无压力的刮油菜Cy.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130923/ae18db37c702a621c97a9e7c0f3fb830.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"秒杀双节，吃货毫无压力的刮油菜Cr.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130923/0cfa6608821cac2892e4ced2fc0cd955.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"秒杀双节，吃货毫无压力的刮油菜Qm.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130923/6dd5f41b98e5a4d38bdfda0e7084b330.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></td></tr><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">熏干竹笋炒尖椒</div></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">竹笋肉片</div></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">凉拌竹笋黄瓜</div></td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　2、白菜</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　白菜含有丰富的膳食纤维，可增强肠胃的蠕动，减少粪便在体内的存留时间，加强消化吸收功能，能够润肠通便，减少体内堆积毒素。白菜中所含的果胶，可以帮助人体排除多余的胆固醇。另外，大白菜含水量丰富，高达95%，所含热量极少，不会导致热量超标而变成脂肪堆积在体内。白菜还含有丰富的维生素C和维生素E，多吃对养颜美容有好处。</p><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"500\" align=\"center\" border=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 24px;\"><tbody style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; text-align: center;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"秒杀双节，吃货毫无压力的刮油菜Cy.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130923/48650d26ab6d3c3969b7e4c57a014f6b.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"秒杀双节，吃货毫无压力的刮油菜Cr.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130923/1bc530fb0ac4a7c6744930feaf50129a.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"秒杀双节，吃货毫无压力的刮油菜Qm.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130923/4731a688c2dd38670c59794dd5c0460d.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></td></tr><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">白菜炖豆腐</div></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">清香手撕圆白菜</div></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">鱼香白菜</div></td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　3、红薯</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　红薯当中有丰富的膳食纤维，帮助促进肠胃蠕动，防止便秘，避免癌变。而且常吃红薯可以帮助维持体内正常叶酸水平，降低患癌风险。</p><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"500\" align=\"center\" border=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 24px;\"><tbody style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; text-align: center;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"秒杀双节，吃货毫无压力的刮油菜Cy.jpg\" src=\"/data/upload/9b/5v/5241b24e09097_600x480.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"秒杀双节，吃货毫无压力的刮油菜Cr.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130923/079faf03990823ac37c39f983467b5ac.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"秒杀双节，吃货毫无压力的刮油菜Qm.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130923/04707e1fedc83860f4dda0c1515b55c4.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></td></tr><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">红薯粥</div></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">红薯山药粥</div></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">烤红薯</div></td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　4、黑木耳</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　黑木耳中富含植物胶质，有很强的吸附能力，可以在短时间内吸附残留于肠道内的肠道垃圾等物质，比如灰尘与杂质，并将其集中起来排出体外，起到清洁血液和洗涤肠道的作用。</p><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"500\" align=\"center\" border=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 24px;\"><tbody style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; text-align: center;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"秒杀双节，吃货毫无压力的刮油菜Cy.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130923/6580a59954d818a967af206cc9cec45a.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"秒杀双节，吃货毫无压力的刮油菜Cr.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130923/eebe6fd4e4a637f738c594a35d16b496.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"秒杀双节，吃货毫无压力的刮油菜Qm.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130923/70736133e3e82bfbec239881c82af75c.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></td></tr><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">凉拌黑木耳</div></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">木耳炒肉</div></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">香菇酱炒豆腐木耳</div></td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　5、芹菜：</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　芹菜含有较多膳食纤维，能促进肠道的蠕动，绝对是一种减肥蔬菜,这是许多人知道的事实。它之所以刮油，也是源于它丰富的粗纤维,可以刮洗肠壁,减少脂肪被小肠吸收等等特别含有降血压成分，也有降血脂、降血糖作用。</p><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"500\" align=\"center\" border=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 24px;\"><tbody style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; text-align: center;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"秒杀双节，吃货毫无压力的刮油菜Cy.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130923/5d77913655cc13702497c1443086c3b3.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"秒杀双节，吃货毫无压力的刮油菜Cr.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130923/3c979eeed46f99092a304d756f04196d.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"秒杀双节，吃货毫无压力的刮油菜Qm.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130923/40bc7d79607ad4adca030e74be3c70ee.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></td></tr><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">凉拌芹菜金针菇</div></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">西芹腰果百合</div></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">芹菜肉丝小炒</div></td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　6、土豆：</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　有很强的降低血中胆固醇、维持血液酸碱平衡、延缓衰老及防癌抗癌作用。土豆含有丰富的膳食纤维和胶质类等容积性排便物质，可谓“肠道清道夫”。</p><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"500\" align=\"center\" border=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 24px;\"><tbody style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; text-align: center;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"秒杀双节，吃货毫无压力的刮油菜Cy.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130923/fb74234a8821482f091ee80ce78fda77.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"秒杀双节，吃货毫无压力的刮油菜Cr.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130923/e12723559ba66f1c7b077bfdb30808e3.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"秒杀双节，吃货毫无压力的刮油菜Qm.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130923/2425f7e1da2dca903f836dd54c176f39.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></td></tr><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">凉拌土豆丝</div></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">酸辣土豆丝</div></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">土豆鸡蛋饼</div></td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　7、海藻：</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　海藻素有“海洋蔬菜”美誉。海藻以其低热量、低脂肪令人瞩目，一些海藻具有降血脂作用。海带等褐藻，含有丰富的胶体纤维，能显著降低血清胆固醇。海藻还含有许多独特的活性物质，具有降压、降脂、降糖、抗癌等作用。</p><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"500\" align=\"center\" border=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 24px;\"><tbody style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; text-align: center;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"秒杀双节，吃货毫无压力的刮油菜Cy.jpg\" src=\"/data/upload/3h/5g/5241b3a627b8f_600x480.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"秒杀双节，吃货毫无压力的刮油菜Cr.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130923/cc241c33e88d70dbe471dd4ecd3713c7.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"秒杀双节，吃货毫无压力的刮油菜Qm.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130923/9b466db91760f3dea5b05b12bc7b9e58.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></td></tr><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">辣炒海带丝</div></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">凉拌海带丝</div></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">三文鱼圆海带汤</div></td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　8、苹果：</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　苹果中除含有丰富的维生素外，其果胶含量也是相当丰富的，具有降低血液中胆固醇的作用。而且苹果含丰富的矿物质钾，可帮助排除体内多余的钠盐，如每天吃2个苹果，对维持血压、血脂均有好处。</p><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"500\" align=\"center\" border=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 24px;\"><tbody style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; text-align: center;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"知悉你的明眸，告别眼睛干痒Cy.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130923/3f0280beeac9a0546dafb4e1cffdcbf7.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"知悉你的明眸，告别眼睛干痒Cr.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130923/e3cd302d56aa299e14fe6b6d8e4c8e99.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"知悉你的明眸，告别眼睛干痒Qm.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130923/74bdbe8b59a0af89fe2cf486ca93922e.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></td></tr><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">苹果玉米汤</div></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">红豆桂圆汤煲苹果</div></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">胡萝卜苹果汁</div></td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　9、玉米：</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　玉米含丰富的钙、磷、镁、铁、硒及维生素A、B1、B2、B6、E和胡萝卜素等，还富含纤维质。常食玉米油，可降低胆固醇并软化血管。玉米对胆囊炎、胆结石、黄疸型肝炎和糖尿病等，有辅助治疗作用。</p><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"500\" align=\"center\" border=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 24px;\"><tbody style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; text-align: center;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"知悉你的明眸，告别眼睛干痒Cy.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130923/f581b0dc1fb745a058a03fa0dbbaad3d.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"知悉你的明眸，告别眼睛干痒Cr.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130923/5b53410ea3535000c2b23d17d1c92b94.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"知悉你的明眸，告别眼睛干痒Qm.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130923/cdfc09ff18606b9c4dae5e4c55f7746c.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></td></tr><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">彩椒玉米鸡丁</div></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">枸杞玉米五彩羹</div></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">玉米面鸡蛋饼</div></td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　10、燕麦：</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　燕麦具备降胆固醇和降血脂的作用。由于燕麦中含有丰富的食物纤维，这种可溶性的燕麦纤维，在其他谷物中找不到。因这种纤维容易被人体吸收，且因热含量低，既有利于减肥，又适合心脏病、高血压和糖尿病人对食疗的需要。</p><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"500\" align=\"center\" border=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 24px;\"><tbody style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; text-align: center;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"知悉你的明眸，告别眼睛干痒Cy.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130923/ae02f42a41043dc540aa54b46df6d1d1.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"知悉你的明眸，告别眼睛干痒Cr.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130923/f59496fda2d4e6097bbda49f6372288e.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"知悉你的明眸，告别眼睛干痒Qm.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130923/b736ce482e736855f05613b68fbac8c2.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></td></tr><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">燕麦蜜豆粥</div></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">奶香红豆燕麦粥</div></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">低脂燕麦饼</div></td></tr></tbody></table>', '', '', '1380037333', '270', '1', '', '', '', '3', '周边小编', '1'), ('26', '秋季最该吃的五种水果', '', '<ul class=\"vcl-top\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 20px; list-style: none; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); width: 658px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px;\"><li class=\"vclt-con\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; text-align: left; clear: both; line-height: 22px;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px auto 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 23px;\">这些天，台风登入广西区域，所有的广西城市忽然温度下降了好多，南宁这个城市也不例外。走在街道边，观看着周边的景点，小编忽然发现天气开始凉了，秋天到了！亲，开始要记得多穿衣服哦，周边网小编提醒您，秋天来了！在看看秋天的季节，我们身边都有哪些美食水果呢？</p><p style=\"margin: 0px auto 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 23px;\"><br /></p><p style=\"margin: 0px auto 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 23px;\">秋天一到，各种色彩诱人、味道鲜美的水果开始陆续上市。它们不仅能起到润秋燥的作用，在营养上还各有优势。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px auto 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 23px;\"><br /></p><p style=\"margin: 0px auto 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 23px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">葡萄，</span>抗氧化之王</span>。葡萄中含的白藜芦醇是一种强抗氧化剂，可抗衰老，并清除体内自由基，对心脑血管病有积极的预防和治疗作用。需要提醒的是，葡萄性寒凉，脾胃虚寒者不宜多食。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px auto 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 23px;\"><img src=\"/data/upload/2g/2z/52452961dff39_600x480.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br /></p><p style=\"margin: 0px auto 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 23px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">山楂</span>，果胶之王</span>。果胶是一种多糖物质，有助于控制血糖和血脂。此外，山楂还含有大量黄酮类化合物和有机酸，具有防癌、抗癌、降血压和胆固醇的作用。一般人群均可食用，尤其适合消化不良者、心血管疾病患者和肠炎患者，但孕妇、儿童、胃酸分泌过多者、病后体虚及牙病患者不宜食用。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px auto 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 23px;\"><br /></p><p style=\"margin: 0px auto 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 23px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">柑橘，</span>维生素B1之王</span>。维生素B1对神经系统的信号传导具有重要作用。此外，柑橘中的类胡萝卜素含量也远远高于其他秋季水果，这种营养素在体内能转化成维生素A，具有护眼明目的作用。柑橘中还含有抗氧化、抗癌、抗过敏成分，并能防止血凝，减少冠心病、中风及高血压的发病率等。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px auto 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 23px;\"><br /></p><p style=\"margin: 0px auto 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 23px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">石榴，</span>膳食纤维之王</span>。石榴富含的水溶性膳食纤维在人体消化道中不会被酶分解，既可以防止便秘，又能缓解腹泻。此外，石榴籽富含大量维生素C、多酚类物质，这些物质有延缓衰老的作用。因此，在吃石榴的时候要嚼嚼籽。需要提醒的是，石榴有收敛作用，便秘的人要少吃。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px auto 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 23px;\"><br /></p><p style=\"margin: 0px auto 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 23px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">鲜枣，</span>全能王</span>。与其他秋季水果相比，鲜枣多项营养素含量均居首位，如维生素C、钾、镁、铁、锌等。维生素C可软化血管、预防高血压、冠心病和动脉硬化，钾对控制血压有利，镁有助于对抗压力等。需要提醒的是，枣偏热，痰多、便秘、胃病患者和糖尿病患者都不宜多吃。</p></li></ul>', '', '', '1380264316', '219', '1', '', '', '', '3', '周边小编', '1'), ('27', '国庆来了吃海鲜的忌讳', '', '<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">期盼已久的国庆假期终于来了，可以好好玩，好好吃啦。喜欢吃海鲜的同学们注意了啊，有8条禁忌是你们必须记牢的!</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"59.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"300\" src=\"/data/upload/9x/2b/524cf82272b28_600x480.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: block; max-width: 550px;\" /></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">1、海鲜煮不熟含有细菌</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　海鲜中的病菌主要是副溶血性弧菌等，耐热性比较强，80℃以上才能杀灭。除了水中带来的细菌之外，海鲜中还可能存在寄生虫卵以及加工带来的病3。海鲜啤酒同吃惹痛风</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　在吃海鲜时最好别饮用啤酒。虾、蟹等海产品在人体代谢后会形成尿酸，而尿酸过多会引起痛风、肾结石等病症。如果大量食用海鲜的同时，再饮用啤酒，就会加速体内尿酸的形成。所以，在大量食用海鲜的时候，千万别喝啤酒，否则会对身体产生不利影响。菌和病毒污染。一般来说，在沸水中煮4-5分钟才算彻底杀菌。因此，在吃“醉蟹”、“生海胆”、“酱油腌海鲜”之类不加热烹调的海鲜一定要慎重，吃生鱼片的时候也要保证鱼的新鲜和卫生。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">2、死贝类病菌毒素多</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　贝类本身带菌量比较高，蛋白质分解又很快，一旦死去便大量繁殖病菌、产生毒素，同时其中所含的不饱和脂肪酸也容易氧化酸败。不新鲜的贝类还会产生较多的胺类和自由基，对人体健康造成威胁。选购活贝之后也不能在家存放太久，要尽快烹调。过敏体质的人尤其应当注意，因为有时候过敏反应不是因为海鲜本身，而是在海鲜蛋白质分解过程中的物质导致的。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">3、海鲜啤酒同吃惹痛风</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　在吃海鲜时最好别饮用啤酒。虾、蟹等海产品在人体代谢后会形成尿酸，而尿酸过多会引起痛风、肾结石等病症。如果大量食用海鲜的同时，再饮用啤酒，就会加速体内尿酸的形成。所以，在大量食用海鲜的时候，千万别喝啤酒，否则会对身体产生不利影响。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">4、海鲜水果同吃会腹痛</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　鱼、虾、蟹等海产品含有丰富的蛋白质和钙等营养素。而水果中含有较多的鞣酸，如果吃完海产品后，马上吃水果，不但影响人体对蛋白质的吸收，海鲜中的钙还会与水果中的鞣酸相结合，形成难溶的钙，会对胃肠道产生刺激，甚至引起腹痛、恶心、呕吐等症状。最好间隔2小时以上再吃。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"60.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"300\" src=\"/data/upload/5o/0j/524cf8354ddeb_600x480.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: block; max-width: 550px;\" /></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">5、吃海鲜后喝茶长结石</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　吃完海鲜不宜喝茶的道理与不宜吃水果的原因类似。因为茶叶中也含有鞣酸，同样能与海鲜中的钙形成难溶的钙。在食用海鲜前或后吃海鲜，都会增加钙与鞣酸相结合的机会。因此，在吃海鲜时最好别喝茶。同理，也是最好间隔2小时以上。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">6、冰鲜虾不可白灼着吃</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　任何海鲜都只有在高度新鲜的状态下才能做成清蒸、白灼之类的菜肴。水产海鲜与肉类不同，它们体内带有很多耐低温的细菌，而且蛋白质分解特别快。如果放在冰箱里多时，虾体的含菌量增大，蛋白质也已经部分变性，产生了胺类物质，无论怎么样都达不到活虾的口感、风味和安全性，当然也就不适合白灼的吃法了。不过，冰鲜的虾可以高温烹炒或煎炸，同时也能呈现出美味噢。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">7、海鲜维C同食会中毒</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　多种海产品，如虾、蟹、蛤、牡蛎等，体内均含有化学元素砷。一般情况下含量很小，但日益严重的环境污染可能使这些动物体内砷的含量达到较高水平。虾体内所含砷的化合价是五价，一般情况下，五价砷对人体是没有害处的。理论上讲，高剂量的维生素C(一次性摄入维生素C超过500毫克)和五价砷经过复杂的化学反应，会转变为有毒的三价砷(即我们常说的“砒霜”)，当三价砷达到一定剂量时可导致人体中毒。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　据专业人士解释，一次性摄入50个中等大小的苹果或30个梨或10个橙子或生吃3斤以上的绿叶蔬菜，才会大剂量地摄入维生素C。如果经过加热烹调过程，食物中的维生素C还会大打折扣。因此，在吃海产品的同时食用水果或青菜，只要不超过上述的量是没有危险的。金属类元素容易沉积在海鲜的头部，所以尽量不要吃虾头、鱼头</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">8、打包来的海鲜要冷藏</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　如果海鲜已经高温彻底烹熟，那么只需马上放入冷藏室，下餐加热后即可食用。如果海鲜并未经过充分加热，但已经死去，那么应当放进冷藏室，下一餐之前化冻，然后彻底加热烹熟，不要再贪恋生鲜口感。由于海鲜类食品的蛋白质质地细腻，分解很快，拿回家之后应当在一天之内食完，不要长时间存放。</p>', '', '', '1380776073', '190', '1', '', '', '', '1', '周边小编', '1'), ('28', '十大名茶的鉴别方法哦', '', '<span style=\"color:#666666;\"><tuihighlight class=\"tuihighlight\" data_cnzz_tui=\"西湖龙井\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; display: inline;\">西湖龙井</tuihighlight><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">、</span><tuihighlight class=\"tuihighlight\" data_cnzz_tui=\"铁观音\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; display: inline;\">铁观音</tuihighlight><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">、碧螺春、</span><tuihighlight class=\"tuihighlight\" data_cnzz_tui=\"信阳毛尖\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; display: inline;\">信阳毛尖</tuihighlight><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">、都匀毛尖、</span><tuihighlight class=\"tuihighlight\" data_cnzz_tui=\"黄山毛峰\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; display: inline;\">黄山毛峰</tuihighlight><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">、六安瓜片、</span><tuihighlight class=\"tuihighlight\" data_cnzz_tui=\"祁门红茶\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; display: inline;\">祁门红茶</tuihighlight><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">、武夷岩茶、君山银针并称我国十大名茶，芳名远播，成为品茗上选。然而近来年十大名茶也出现了很多假冒产品，下面给大家介绍这些名茶的主要特征和识假方法。</span><br style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\" /><br style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\" /><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1、</span><tuihighlight class=\"tuihighlight\" data_cnzz_tui=\"西湖龙井\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; display: inline;\">西湖龙井</tuihighlight><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">，产于浙江杭州西湖区，</span><tuihighlight class=\"tuihighlight\" data_cnzz_tui=\"茶叶\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; display: inline;\">茶叶</tuihighlight><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">为扁形，叶细嫩，条形整齐，宽度一致，为绿黄色，手感光滑，一芽一叶或二叶；芽长于叶，一般长3厘米以下，芽叶均匀成朵，不带夹蒂、碎片，小巧玲珑。龙井茶味道清香，假冒龙井茶则多是清草味，夹蒂较多，手感不光滑。</span><br style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\" /><br style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\" /><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2、碧螺春，产于江苏吴县太湖的洞庭山碧螺峰。银芽显露，一芽一叶，</span><tuihighlight class=\"tuihighlight\" data_cnzz_tui=\"茶叶\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; display: inline;\">茶叶</tuihighlight><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">总长度为1．5厘米，每500克有5.8万－7万个芽头，芽为白豪卷曲形，叶为卷曲清绿色，叶底幼嫩，均匀明亮。假的为一芽二叶，芽叶长度不齐，呈黄色。</span><br style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\" /><br style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\" /><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3、</span><tuihighlight class=\"tuihighlight\" data_cnzz_tui=\"信阳毛尖\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; display: inline;\">信阳毛尖</tuihighlight><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">，产于河南信阳车云山。其外形条索紧细、圆、光、直，银绿隐翠，内质香气新鲜，叶底嫩绿匀整，清黑色，一般一芽一叶或一芽二叶，假的为卷曲形，叶片发黄。</span><br style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\" /><br style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\" /></span><p><span style=\"color:#666666;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4、君山银针，产于湖南岳阳君山。由未展开的肥嫩芽头制成，芽头肥壮挺直、匀齐，满披茸毛，色泽金黄光亮，香气清鲜，茶色浅黄，味甜爽，冲泡看起来芽尖冲向水面，悬空竖立，然后徐徐下沉杯底，形如群笋出土，又像银刀直立。假银针为清草味，泡后银针不能竖立</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">。</span></p><p><span style=\"color:#666666;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><img src=\"/data/upload/9j/1v/52517bd54625e_600x480.png\" alt=\"\" /></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#666666;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><br /></span></span></p><span style=\"color:#666666;\"><br style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\" /><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;5、六安瓜片，产于安徽六安和金寨两县的齐云山。其外形平展，每一片不带芽和茎梗，叶呈绿色光润，微向上重叠，形似瓜子，内质香气清高，水色碧绿，滋味回甜，叶底厚实明亮。假的则味道较苦，色比较黄。</span><br style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\" /><br style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\" /><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;6、</span><tuihighlight class=\"tuihighlight\" data_cnzz_tui=\"黄山毛峰\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; display: inline;\">黄山毛峰</tuihighlight><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">，产于安徽歙县黄山。其外形细嫩稍卷曲，芽肥壮、匀齐，有锋毫，形状有点像“雀舌”，叶呈金黄色；色泽嫩绿油润，香气清鲜，水色清澈、杏黄、明亮，味醇厚、回甘，叶底芽叶成朵，厚实鲜艳。假茶呈土黄，味苦，叶底不成朵。</span><br style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\" /><br style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\" /><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;7、</span><tuihighlight class=\"tuihighlight\" data_cnzz_tui=\"祁门红茶\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; display: inline;\">祁门红茶</tuihighlight><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">，产于安徽祁门县。茶颜色为棕红色，切成0.6－0.8厘米，味道浓厚，强烈醇和、鲜爽。假茶一般带有人工色素，味苦涩、淡薄，条叶形状不齐。</span><br style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\" /><br style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\" /></span><p><span style=\"color:#666666;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;8、都匀毛尖，产于贵州都匀县。</span><tuihighlight class=\"tuihighlight\" data_cnzz_tui=\"茶叶\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; display: inline;\">茶叶</tuihighlight><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">嫩绿匀齐，细小短薄，一芽一叶初展，形似雀舌，长2一2.5厘米，外形条索紧细、卷曲，毫毛显露，色泽绿润、内质香气清嫩、新鲜、回甜，水色清澈，叶底嫩绿匀齐。假</span><tuihighlight class=\"tuihighlight\" data_cnzz_tui=\"茶叶\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; display: inline;\">茶叶</tuihighlight><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">底不匀，味苦。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#666666;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><img src=\"/data/upload/4m/2n/52517c53c7194_600x480.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br /></span></span></p><span style=\"color:#666666;\"><br style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\" /><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;9、</span><tuihighlight class=\"tuihighlight\" data_cnzz_tui=\"铁观音\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; display: inline;\">铁观音</tuihighlight><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">，产于福建安溪县。叶体沉重如铁，形美如观音，多呈螺旋形，色泽砂绿，光润，绿蒂，具有天然兰花香，汤色清澈金黄，味醇厚甜美，入口微苦，立即转甜，耐冲泡，叶底开展，青绿红边，肥厚明亮，每颗茶都带茶枝，假</span><tuihighlight class=\"tuihighlight\" data_cnzz_tui=\"茶叶\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; display: inline;\">茶叶</tuihighlight><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">形长而薄，条索较粗，无青翠红边，叶泡三遍后便无香味。</span><br style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\" /><br style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\" /><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;10、武夷岩茶，产于福建崇安县。外形条索肥壮、紧结、匀整，带扭曲条形，俗称“晴蜒头”，叶背起蛙皮状砂粒，俗称蛤蟆背，内质香气馥郁、隽永，滋味醇厚回苦，润滑爽口，汤色橙黄，清澈艳丽，叶底匀亮，边缘朱红或起红点，中央叶肉黄绿色，叶脉浅黄色，耐泡6－8次以上，假茶开始味淡，欠韵味，色泽枯暗。</span></span>', '', '', '1381072002', '227', '1', '', '', '', '1', '周边小编', '1'), ('29', '一起看那N道风味炒饭', '', '锅铲铿锵的节奏与不时窜出的烟雾香气，伴随在锅中不断跳跃、翻滚的米粒。。在如此淬炼之下，白米饭和各种食材融为一体，摇身一变，成为粒粒晶亮分明、喷香诱人，略带烟火味的风味炒饭，温饱了多少吃货的胃和心啊~<p>　　<strong>一、鱼香炒饭</strong></p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"鱼香炒饭.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131010/8a6341c1abd69c7707fbcbc91f5e0fe1.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"550\" /></p><p>　　材料：</p><p>　　剩米饭1碗、鸡脯肉1小块、洋葱适量、绿尖椒适量、胡萝卜适量、俺个人口味添加用量)葱姜蒜末、干红辣椒(或者郫县豆瓣酱)、料酒、糖、盐、白醋、鸡精、淀粉、酱油</p><p>　　做法：</p><p>　　1、洋葱、尖椒、胡萝卜切成小丁。</p><p>　　2、鸡脯肉切小丁，用淀粉、酱油和料酒挂浆(这样处理肉肉炒出来会比较嫩滑)。</p><p>　　3、锅中倒油烧热，下葱姜蒜末、干红辣椒(或者郫县豆瓣酱)爆香。</p><p>　　4、放鸡肉丁炒散。</p><p>　　5、倒入洋葱和胡萝卜丁略炒。</p><p>　　6、加料酒(少许)、糖、盐、白醋调味。</p><p>　　<strong>二、鲜蔬炒饭</strong></p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"鲜蔬炒饭.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131010/a7037717e16d02f79835de5a3da9a562.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"550\" /></p><p>　　材料：南瓜一块，玉米粒一大勺，红萝卜一根，菜心几根，鸡蛋两个，米饭一碗，油少许，盐少许，酱油几滴</p><p>　　做法：</p><p>　　1、南瓜切和玉米超不多大小的粒粒，胡萝卜切丝，菜心去叶子留梗切丁</p><p>　　2、锅里烧开水，菜心粒，玉米，南瓜丁入锅焯水捞出备用</p><p>　　3、锅里热少许油，倒入刚刚焯水的鲜蔬丁，炒片刻，调入盐入味，装起备用</p><p>　　4、锅里继续放入少许油，打入鸡蛋，炒散，倒入米饭，继续翻炒散至一粒粒散开</p><p>　　5、加入几滴酱油，再次炒均匀，放入精盐调味，加入红萝卜丝，然后倒入鲜蔬粒，全部炒均匀即可出锅!享用</p><p>　　6、如果需要摆造型什么的，用个碗装起，压实，然后倒扣，取走碗即可!</p><p>　　<strong>三、红烧牛肉炒饭</strong></p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"红烧牛肉炒饭.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131010/c1d0c72df71d9d4fe0acd27fa0b8e119.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"551\" /></p><p>　　材料：剩米饭 剩的红烧牛肉+汤汁 胡萝卜 土豆 芥兰梗(或香芹、蒜薹)、盐(酌情)</p><p>　　做法：</p><p>　　1、土豆、胡萝卜皆去皮切丁，土豆丁冲去淀粉沥干。芥兰梗切丁;</p><p>　　2、红烧牛肉切成小一点的块;</p><p>　　3、锅中倒油，中小火将胡萝卜和土豆丁煸至边缘微焦;</p><p>　　4、倒入芥兰梗翻炒几下，此时可调入少许盐，以利蔬菜入味;</p><p>　　5、倒入牛肉翻炒均匀;</p><p>　　6、倒入米饭翻松，然后倒入适量红烧牛肉汁，炒匀。出锅前酌情调入盐，翻炒均匀即可。</p><p>　　<strong>四、杏鲍菇咖喱炒饭</strong></p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"杏鲍菇咖喱炒饭.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131010/a5341af5d6d1befeddc992f9759a3de7.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"551\" /></p><p>　　材料：米饭50g、杏鲍菇30g、青椒15g 、红椒15g 、甜豌豆30g、甘蓝20g、咖喱粉一小勺、食盐适量、橄榄油2大勺</p><p>　　做法：</p><p>　　1、所有配菜洗净，切小丁，甜豌豆化冻备用。</p><p>　　2、炒锅烧热后倒入橄榄油，放入杏鲍菇煸炒，炒软后放入甘蓝，再放入青红椒豌豆炒匀。</p><p>　　3、把米饭放入锅中，用铲子轻碾，使之分散，与蔬菜炒匀。</p><p>　　4、放入一小勺咖喱粉和适量食盐翻炒，使炒饭均匀呈现咖喱黄即可关火。</p><p>　　<strong>五、韩式泡菜炒饭</strong></p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"韩式泡菜炒饭.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131010/66f615a24c1088681b258f292fc9f23a.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"550\" /></p><p>　　材料：韩国泡菜、猪肉丝、白米饭、葱、盐、淀粉</p><p>　　做法：</p><p>　　1、韩国泡菜切成细丝。猪肉丝用泡菜汁、一点点淀粉拌匀腌制。葱切葱花;</p><p>　　2、热锅温油倒入泡菜丝和腌制好的猪肉丝一起中火翻炒两分钟;</p><p>　　3、倒入白米饭，边不断翻炒边把米饭打散，炒两分钟左右，至米饭呈散开干爽状态;</p><p>　　4、加一点点盐炒匀后，撒上葱花出锅;</p><p>　　<strong>六、鸡丁炒饭</strong></p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"鸡丁炒饭.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131010/43c7e26dc9f224092e302a13d5f21347.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"550\" /></p><p>　　材料：米饭、鸡肉、彩椒、青椒、鸡蛋、淀粉、香葱、洋葱、生抽、食盐、食用油、蚝油</p><p>　　做法：</p><p>　　1、鸡胸肉适量洗净备用;</p><p>　　2、彩椒、青椒、香葱和洋葱洗净备用;</p><p>　　3、按人口量准备米饭备用;</p><p>　　4、鸡蛋适量;</p><p>　　5、鸡肉切小丁备用;</p><p>　　6、将鸡肉丁装入碗中，加入少许食盐、淀粉和蛋清一起腌制起来;</p><p>　　7、将彩椒、洋葱和青椒切丁备用;</p><p>　　8、香葱切碎备用;</p><p>　　9、鸡蛋加入少许食盐打散备用;</p><p>　　10、炒锅放油，将鸡蛋炒熟铲出备用;</p><p>　　11、鸡肉丁放入锅内翻炒;</p><p>　　12、鸡肉炒至变色即可;</p><p>　　13、下入洋葱翻炒，同时放入食盐、五香粉、蚝油和生抽;</p><p>　　14、下入彩椒和青椒、洋葱翻炒;</p><p>　　15、炒菜入味后，放入米饭翻炒;</p><p>　　16、最后放入炒好的鸡蛋，翻炒均匀，出锅前撒入香葱，即可装碗食用;</p><p>　　<strong>七、苋菜炒饭</strong></p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"苋菜炒饭.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131010/9a0cc29847c0fcf94c19aee6d1c0b950.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"550\" /></p><p>　　材料：苋菜300克、米饭300克、蒜、盐、蚝油</p><p>　　做法：</p><p>　　1、苋菜洗净，切小段;</p><p>　　2、蒜切末;</p><p>　　3、锅中入少许油，放入蒜末炒香;</p><p>　　4、倒入苋菜，调入盐、蚝油略翻炒;</p><p>　　5、倒入大米饭翻炒均匀即可;</p><p>　<strong>　八、酱油炒饭</strong></p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"酱油炒饭.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131010/739af9917b5be3a564472c6e7b28b3aa.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"550\" /></p><p>　　材料：剩米饭、胡萝卜、鲜豌豆、鸡蛋、小葱、猪油、食用油、老抽、盐</p><p>　　做法：</p><p>　　1、将鲜豌豆倒入锅中的清水中；</p><p>　　2、大火煮开；</p><p>　　3、鲜豌豆很好熟，煮个2、3分钟就熟了，用笊篱捞出；</p><p>　　4、立刻放入冰水中，可以保持豌豆的绿色；</p><p>　　4、将胡萝卜切成小丁，小葱切成葱花，葱白和葱叶分开；</p><p>　　5、挖一勺猪油放入加热的锅子中；</p><p>　　6、猪油融化后，转小火，先将葱白丁放入慢慢煸出葱香味；</p><p>　　7、然后将滑散的鸡蛋液倒入；</p><p>　　8、蛋液刚刚开始凝固时；</p><p>　　9、用木铲迅速滑散，成鸡蛋丁；</p><p>　　10、稍微再炒炒，盛出；</p><p>　　11、重新加入少许食用油，烧至5成热时，将胡萝卜丁倒入；</p><p>　　12、小火，将胡萝卜丁翻炒几下；</p><p>　　13、放入煮熟的鲜豌豆；</p><p>　　14、稍加一点点盐，因为后面炒米饭中还要放老抽，所以此步请根据自己口味酌情添加；</p><p>　　15、将米饭放入；</p><p>　　16、调入老抽。不要一下子倒很多，可以先少倒一点，不够再加；</p><p>　　17、翻炒均匀，让每一粒大米饭都均匀裹上酱油；</p><p>　　18、将之前炒好的鸡蛋碎倒入；</p><p>　　19、炒炒，洒入小葱花，出锅；</p><p>　　<strong>九、开胃剁椒炒饭</strong></p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"开胃剁椒炒饭.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131010/340882bcabbe6b677ad51de5c30fdf18.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"550\" /></p><p>　　材料：剩饭1小碗、鸡蛋2个、剁椒适量、盐少许、鸡精少许</p><p>　　准备：</p><p>　　蛋液打散，充分搅打均匀;</p><p>　　做法：</p><p>　　1、锅中加油，烧热后倒入蛋液;</p><p>　　2、迅速用锅铲滑散，倒入剩米饭，用铲子压散;</p><p>　　3、加入适量剁椒;</p><p>　　4、再加入少许鸡精和盐，翻炒均匀即可。</p><p>　　<strong>十、菠萝炒饭</strong></p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"菠萝炒饭.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131010/ccc5c5a17159d1150cf257aabde56381.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"550\" /></p><p>　　材料：成熟菠萝1个，隔夜米饭1大碗，鸡腿1个，红椒丁，胡萝卜丁，青豆，玉米粒，香葱少许，色拉油，生抽，胡椒粉，料酒，盐，鸡粉适量</p><p>　　做法：</p><p>　　1、准备好所有材料;</p><p>　　2、鸡腿剔骨去皮后切成小丁，加生抽，胡椒粉及少许料酒腌一会儿;</p><p>　　3、菠萝纵向一切二半;</p><p>　　4、用小刀在切开的菠萝上横竖各切出均匀的刀口，注意深度不要切透了，用勺子将菠萝肉取出泡在盐水里，并将菠萝壳修成光滑的小碗;</p><p>　　5、胡萝卜丁，青豆，玉米粒分别过水焯熟;</p><p>　　6、炒锅置火上，加适量油爆香葱后将腌好的鸡肉炒熟后盛出;</p><p>　　7、再倒入少许油，将香葱炒香;</p><p>　　8、倒入米饭翻炒;</p><p>　　9、倒入焯好的青豆;</p><p>　　10、倒入焯好的胡萝卜丁;</p><p>　　11、翻炒均匀后将鸡腿丁加入翻炒;</p><p>　　12、加适量的盐及鸡粉调味翻炒;</p><p>　　13、倒入焯好的玉米粒;</p><p>　　14、加香葱;</p><p>　　15、菠萝烫泡好后控干水分也倒入炒饭中;</p><p>　　16、翻炒均匀即可出锅装入菠萝小碗中开吃吧;</p><p>　　<strong>十一、蛋炒饭</strong></p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"11.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131010/3596968704ce6ce7a01c0ecb754ead20.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"500\" /></p><p>　　材料：熟米饭一碗、甜豌豆、玉米粒、青红椒粒、鸡蛋两个、葱蒜少许、盐。</p><p>　　做法：</p><p>　　1、鸡蛋打散，放少许盐，锅中放油，油热后放入打散的鸡蛋翻炒，盛出;</p><p>　　2、炒锅中放油，油热后爆香蒜片和葱花;</p><p>　　3、放入玉米和豌豆粒翻炒;</p><p>　　4、放入青红椒粒翻炒;</p><p>　　5、放入米饭和炒熟的鸡蛋翻炒;</p><p>　　6、改为中小火慢慢翻炒，米饭会一粒粒散开。放入盐调味即可关火;</p><p>　　7、把蛋炒饭盛盘子里面，整理成心形的，用紫饭菜粒围边即可</p>', '', '', '1382600686', '175', '1', '', '', '', '1', '周边小编', '1'), ('30', '素菜能吃出肉的味道来', '', '<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;老听朋友们聊天，吃素健康，可是又想念肉的味道... 呵呵，今天，周边小编来告诉你，别以为没肉吃就跟没救了似的，素菜照样可以吃的有滋有味~ 的嘛</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;【卤素鸡】</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">卤水菜式，无论荤素都尽显其厚重的内涵，想不到的完美滋味。</span></span></p><center style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"0cebf1afg7c9d9b566b86&amp;690.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131125/5ac3f6b2b1880729580e94ad54c7a0f9.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"450\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></center><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　材料：素鸡2个</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　配料：葱1根，姜4片，花椒1小撮，八角一颗，干红辣椒5个，卤水汁3大勺，白糖1大勺，花雕酒2勺</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　1.将素鸡洗净切成1厘米厚的薄片</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　2.不粘锅中油热后放入素鸡片，小火慢煎</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　3.煎至两面微黄即可夹出待用，要让素鸡里面既能煎透外表面还不焦</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　4.锅中油热先放入干辣椒，小火煸炒至颜色发暗并有辣味冒出，再放葱、姜、花椒、八角煸炒至香</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　5.加入足够多的开水，在加入卤水汁3大勺、白糖1大勺、花雕酒2勺，煮开后放入素鸡</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　6.大火煮开后，中小火卤煮半个小时，至汤汁收浓香味浓厚时即可关火</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">【咖喱蘑菇】</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">咖喱跟很多食材配都很好吃，我喜欢配蘑菇或者块茎类的食材，跟着咖喱炖的极其入味，吸足了咖喱的精华但还保持着筋道的口感。</span></span></p><center style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"001jbRXLty6DNozJOxZ8b&amp;690.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131125/2fc0dbc146076b4c27eff68e5eb71a0a.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"450\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></center><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　原料：蘑菇，红椒，咖喱酱(也可以用咖喱块)如果酱汁有味道了就不用加太多盐调味了</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　1.红椒切块、大蒜切片，口蘑洗净，做锅清水，水开后将蘑菇下锅，略微焯一下，也就是略煮1钟捞出控干待用</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　2.锅内放入少许橄榄油，放入红椒和蒜片煸炒出香味</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　3.放入咖喱酱，炒出香味和黄金色</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　4.放入蘑菇，继续翻翻炒炒</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　5.直至每个蘑菇都包裹上咖喱，放上一小碗水大火烧开咖喱酱搅拌开，转小火，盖盖慢慢炖，直至蘑菇入味</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　6.炖的时候也可以放入小砂锅炖，吃的时候烧个小蜡烛烘烤着，更好，咖喱是越熬越浓。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">【酱烤杏鲍菇】</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">杏鲍菇被称为“平菇王”，口感鲜嫩，煎烤着吃甚是美味，如果用生菜卷着吃是极好不过的了，跟烤肉比起来有过之而无不及。杏鲍菇腌好后放在冰箱里，随时想吃随时都可以取出来煎烤，五分钟就能烤一盘，懒人最爱~</span></span></p><center style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"4ba904a6hc08d02f7e390&amp;690.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131125/8f45392fb0f9936647a410a551a7c005.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"450\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></center><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　原料：杏鲍菇4颗，花生油，酱香烤肉料</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　1.杏鲍菇摘洗干净，用厨房纸巾抹干水分</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　2.顺长切成薄厚适中的片</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　3.将烤肉酱倒入料盒底部</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　4.排进一层杏鲍菇片，让杏鲍菇两面都抹上烤肉酱，再放上一层杏鲍菇</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　5.再倒上一层烤肉酱</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　6.以此类推，将杏鲍菇都排进料盒，抹上烤肉酱，腌制半小时以上</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　7.平底锅抹薄薄一层油，烧热后放入腌好的杏鲍菇片</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　8.煎至两面金黄，撒上少许迷迭香后出锅</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">【粉蒸芋头】</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">粉糯的芋头，五香味儿的米粉，开胃的剁椒，香浓的滋味别有一番风情。</span></span></p><center style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"4fb121fbtx6CB0dzIkEa8&amp;690.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131125/066bb9fffec9e38b27034289fbe60569.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"450\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></center><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　用料：大米300克，糯米50克，五香粉1.5小匙;芋头约300克;剁椒一大匙</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　调料：大蒜末，葱花，盐适量，酱油一大匙，白糖0.5小匙，油一大匙</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　1.将大米与糯米放入锅内(不用放油)，小火慢炒;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　2.炒至大米变黄，闻起来有香味后关火晾凉;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　3.放入搅拌机中，磨碎成粉;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　4.加入适量的盐与五香粉，拌匀，待用;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　5.芋头去皮洗净，切滚刀块;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　6.放入酱油、盐、白糖、油，拌匀，腌至约30分钟;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　7.放入三大匙先前磨好的米粉，拌匀;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　8.将粘满米粉的芋头铺在耐热的碗中，放入蒜末与剁椒;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　9.高压锅中放入适量的水，摆入蒸架，将芋头放入高压锅中，盖严锅盖，大火烧至冒气后转中火蒸约15分钟后关火，待高压锅泄压后打开锅盖，撒入葱花即可。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">【干锅土豆】</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">这两年在东北比较流行的一道菜，用小锅盛着端上来，小锅下面点上酒精炉子，一会功夫香气就窜了上来，沾满了调料的土豆外酥里软，确实是一道很好吃的素菜~</span></span></p><center style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"5c6213d1gx6CHJwyxq3e3&amp;690.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131125/cd9bd0bc819d60e3007909bcce799ab2.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"450\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></center><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　原料:土豆(马铃薯)300克，干淀粉60克，面粉20克，辣椒粉2小勺(根据自己的口味增减)，孜然粉或者孜然粒2小勺，花椒粉1小勺，葱姜蒜末各适量，盐适量，1里面左右的香菜段一小把</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　1.土豆去皮洗净切成0.6—0.8里面的厚片，放入沸水锅里加一小勺盐中小火大约煮3分钟，用筷子扎一下看看刚刚熟了就可以了</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　2.捞出沥干水分，并晾到不烫手，取一个容器，将淀粉和面粉放入，然后用水调成流动缓慢的稍微厚一点的面糊，将晾好的土豆放入轻轻地抓拌，让土豆的表面都沾上面糊</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　3.煎锅烧热倒油，晃一下将锅底铺满，将土豆一片片的摆到锅里煎上色，翻面，再往锅里淋点油将两面都煎上色，如果土豆片多，可以分2—3次将土豆都煎完</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　4.将所有煎好的土豆片都倒入锅中，放入葱姜蒜末和辣椒粉、孜然粉、花椒粉、一小勺盐开中火不停地翻炒，直到所有调料的香味都散发出来，喜欢味精和鸡精的也可以放一些</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　5.然后放入香菜炒匀后关火就可以了</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　6.家里有酒精煲仔锅的可以将锅底垫放点油，然后铺一层例如生菜、包菜、白菜或油菜这样的生蔬菜，然后将煎好的土豆撒上调料拌匀倒入锅中上面撒上香菜就可以上桌了</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">【蟹黄豆腐】</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">味道鲜香爽滑，最主要这样的口感与味道，深受孩子们的喜好，端上桌黄白相间深深的一大盘，色泽就很诱人，一勺下肚，唇齿留香的让人久久回味。</span></span></p><center style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"5f54fb1ftde72636b5675&amp;690.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131125/29b4493042498c8401f80b377ceeb54c.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"450\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></center><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　原料：嫩豆腐或绢豆腐1块，大概300g，咸鸭蛋黄4个</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　辅料：盐3g，葱2根，橄榄油20ml，湿淀粉：40ml</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　1.准备好嫩豆腐和咸鸭蛋黄</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　2.嫩豆腐切小块，锅中放入适量水，烧开后，加入切小块的豆腐丁，放1克盐，煮至冒泡</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　3.捞出豆腐丁，控干水分</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　4.咸鸭蛋蛋黄放入蒸锅中，蒸熟透</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　5.晾凉后的咸鸭蛋黄，用勺背压碎，尽可能的压细碎</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　6.锅中放入橄榄油，放入咸蛋黄碎，用中小火炒均匀，炒出香味(尽可能的炒细腻均匀)</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　7.之后加入豆腐丁，轻轻的翻拌均匀</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　8.加入水淀粉勾芡，翻炒均匀至浓稠</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　9.最后放剩余的2克盐，拌匀即可盛出，撒上葱花即可</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">【软炸蘑菇】</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">家里没肉、嘴馋又想吃肉的情况下，您不妨来上一盘软炸蘑菇。炸好之后趁热吃，外酥里嫩极具肉香，两块下肚，保你心满意足。</span></span></p><center style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"44ca8915tx6DzPfV15q5c&amp;690.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131125/59e186d1eefe0c20638a527beed612be.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"450\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></center><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　原料：鲜嫩的平菇，鸡蛋，土豆淀粉，椒盐</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　1.鸡蛋液搅匀，然后添加土豆淀粉，再次搅打均匀</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　2.平菇去掉根部，清洗之后，入开水中轻微焯一下</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　3.捞出过凉，挤干水分，大块的蘑菇手撕成小块</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　4.蘑菇入面糊中搅拌均匀</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　5.锅内放植物油，烧热，油热后，分次下入挂好糊的蘑菇，蘑菇迅速浮起后，把粘连在一起的分开</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　6.中火炸至秒皮硬，捞起控油</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　7.待油温升高，下入蘑菇复炸一次，变色后马上捞起，控油(或用厨房专用纸吸油)后装盘</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　8.撒上椒盐，趁热食用</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">【红烧腐竹】</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">老少皆宜的大众养生菜。其中的主要原料：腐竹、木耳、胡萝卜，都是对健康有益的食材。加入蚝油后的红烧腐竹，色泽红亮、更加的鲜香浓郁。</span></span></p><center style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"5188c47dg79a23e423f5e&amp;690.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131125/58088e43e12b6cf204496e583ec93d55.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"450\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></center><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　材料：泡发的腐竹300g，泡发的木耳100g，胡萝卜50g</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　配料：葱，姜，蒜，料酒，酱油，糖，蚝油适量</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　1.腐竹、黑木耳提前泡发好，将腐竹切成斜段，胡萝卜切片，葱姜蒜切片</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　2.锅中加少量油烧热，爆香葱姜蒜片</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　3.下入腐竹、木耳、胡萝卜翻炒</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　4.加入适量料酒、酱油、糖及半杯水稍微炖煮片刻</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　5.待汤汁收浓时，加入适量蚝油</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　6.翻炒均匀即可出锅了</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">【宫保杏鲍菇】</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">很好吃、很下饭，色泽红亮、麻辣鲜香...杏鲍菇虽非肉却胜似肉的感觉，加上酥脆的黄飞红麻辣花生、鲜甜多汁的大葱丁，每一口都能感受出不同层次的口感，让人在不知不觉中就又多吃了一碗米饭……</span></span></p><center style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"5188c47dgbf98c88869bf&amp;690.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131125/c42903e5afba7846c3c15e55a28f3bc3.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"442\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></center><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　材料：杏鲍菇300g，大葱丁 100g，黄飞红麻辣花生100g，大蒜2瓣，红尖椒适量，黄飞红麻辣花生中的花椒辣椒1大勺</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　调料：淀粉，料酒，生抽，老抽，醋，糖，盐，味精，胡椒粉，香油</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　1.杏鲍菇，大葱切成同样的丁，蒜切末;将生抽、老抽、料酒、糖各1汤匙+醋2汤匙+盐、味精、香油适量+淀粉、水适量+蒜末1小勺，兑成一个碗汁备用</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　2.将杏鲍菇丁放盆里，撒少许盐静置5分钟后撒入2汤匙淀粉或炸粉，来回晃动，使淀粉附着均匀</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　3.平底锅中加适量油烧热，放入杏鲍菇丁，铺平，先不要翻动，待底面变黄定型后再翻面煎至金黄即可盛出沥油</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　4.锅中留少量油，下入1大勺黄飞红中的花椒辣椒料，小火炒香后，加入蒜末、红尖椒、大葱段</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　5.加入煎好的杏鲍菇丁，倒入事先调好的碗汁，快速翻动</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　6.最后加入黄飞红麻辣花生，拌匀即可装盘</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">【回锅藕片】</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">藕是很好的食材，生吃能清热生津，解渴止呕。熟食性能补益脾胃，温补止泻。烹饪方法多样，不管是炖汤，清炒，凉拌，还是烧，卤，煎，煮，炸，样样行。</span></span></p><center style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"60739de8x7b49d108cd13&amp;690.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131125/5833871b16b6560cd9051183f7b6b05f.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"450\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></center><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　用料：莲藕，青椒，红椒，姜，生粉，豆瓣酱，甜面酱，料酒，白砂糖</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　1.莲藕去皮洗净，切成0.3厘米的厚片。小米椒切圈，大葱，老姜切末</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　2.烧一锅开水，放入藕片氽烫2分钟左右，捞出沥干水分，撒上生粉拌匀</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　3.锅中放入油，油温6成热时，放入藕片炸至表面微焦后，捞出沥油</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　4.锅中留少许底油，放入葱姜末炒香，倒入豆瓣酱炒至出红油，加入甜面酱炒匀</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　5.加入切好的青红椒炒至断生</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　6.倒入藕片，加青红椒，料酒，生抽，白砂糖略炒，起锅即可</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">【茄子豆角】</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">酱香浓郁的下饭菜，除了油大一点，真是无可挑剔了~</span></span></p><center style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"67202f09gdc57e92a11eb&amp;690.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131125/4ecbd0a91cdeb5175a1d2203e45b4a73.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"450\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></center><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　原料：茄子，豆角，姜，蒜，干红辣椒</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　调料：生抽，蚝油</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　1.豆角择去老筋，洗净切段</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　2.茄子洗净，切长条</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　3.干辣椒切段，姜切片</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　4.锅中热油，先放入豆角炸透至表皮褶皱后盛出</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　5.再放入茄子炸透后盛出</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　6.锅中留少许底油，爆香姜、蒜和干辣椒</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　7.放入茄子和豆角翻炒一会儿</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　8.最后调入生抽、蚝油即可</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">【干煸茶树菇】</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">茶树菇是很有韧劲的蘑菇，干煸过味道更为纯粹，下饭吃也很香。虽然是素，但是营养丰富，绝对是大自然赐予人类很好的礼物。</span></span></p><center style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"47822805tx6DhtkkGTXf5&amp;690.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131125/4ba866e961bd54e6782145175d5703bf.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"450\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></center><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　原料：茶树菇，小红辣椒，葱，蒜，大料，小茴香，老抽，盐，糖，少许料酒</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　1.葱、蒜切末，干辣椒椒剪成小段，茶树菇洗净用淡盐水泡10分钟再用清水冲洗干净</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　2.锅内放油煸香葱蒜末，放入小红辣椒煸炒出香味</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　3.放入洗净去蒂的茶树菇</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　4.煸炒茶树菇，直至茶树菇变蔫，倒入老抽，料酒、盐和一点白糖</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　5.继续煸炒至茶树菇收汁，全部吸入到茶树菇内盛出即可</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">【麻辣五香豆干】</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">豆腐又酥又香，隐隐带着香料的气息，配上浇盖的葱，蒜又别有一番滋味。</span></span></p><center style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"u65063762_13cdf21d962g86_b.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131125/5363589f5c3e98da33bd390ebe199c41.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"450\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></center><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　材料： 白豆干10片，新鲜红椒1颗，小葱2根，大蒜3瓣</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　卤水香料： 八角2颗，香叶1片，桔皮1小块，花椒20颗，生抽2大匙，糖1小匙，盐1/4小匙，白胡椒粉1/4小匙，十三香粉1/4小匙</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　浇盖调料： 盐1/4小匙，生抽1小匙，白糖1/4小匙</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　1.将白豆干双面割上斜花刀，红椒、香葱、大蒜剁碎备用;平底锅烧热，放入2大匙油烧热，将豆腐放入用中火煎制</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　2.煎至表面金黄色时，用筷子翻面再煎，直至两面煎到金黄色;把豆腐拨到旁边，下入花椒，八角，香叶，桔皮，炒香</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　3.加入清水或高汤，水量刚没过豆腐块。加入生抽，盐，白糖，胡椒粉，十三香粉调味</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　4.加盖大火煮开后，转小火焖制，直至水份完全收干。将豆腐盛出备用</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　5.炒锅另热少许油，加入剁碎的红椒，小葱，大蒜炒香，加入盐，生抽，白糖，再烧制1分钟即可;将炒好的浇盖料淋在卤好的豆腐干上即可</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">【豆豉辣椒炒荷包蛋】</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">严格来讲这道菜并不算素菜，但是实在很好吃，且做法简单，小编觉得还是有必要秀出来让大家学学^(oo)^ 鸡蛋还可以换成鹌鹑蛋，还省的切了~</span></span></p><center style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"67a261eegcca203acabc3&amp;690.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131125/2edd8047b35d741c33d1a9c0976c01dd.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"450\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /></center><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　原料：鸡蛋4个，豆豉1汤匙，青椒3个，小米辣3个，大蒜2粒，生姜少许，酱油1/2汤匙，盐少许，花生油</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　1、将辣椒洗净，切成段，姜切末，蒜切片。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　2、锅烧热，放油，打入鸡蛋两面煎熟透。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　3、逐一煎好。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　4、把煎好的蛋，切成小块。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　5、锅内放少许油，加入姜蒜、豆豉炒香。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　6、放入辣椒。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　7、加入能让辣椒变咸的少许盐，炒香。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　8、放入切好的煎蛋。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　9、放一点酱油翻炒，使鸡蛋滋润入味。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　10、装盘享用。</p>', '', '', '1385474392', '118', '1', '', '', '', '1', '周边小编', '1');
INSERT INTO `articles` VALUES ('31', '中国人早上都吃些什么', '', '<div class=\"zt_con1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 12px;\"><div class=\"con1_conw\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 30px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; width: 930px;\"><h1 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 16px 0px 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; line-height: 40px; height: 40px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;看不同地区的中国人早上都吃什么？</h1><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 28px; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">古语有云：一天之计在于晨。记得小时候在家乡，每天早上起来都能在桌上发现妈妈买来的</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 28px; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">热气腾腾的一碗豆浆，</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 28px; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">旁边有时放着两根金黄的油条，或者是几个白白胖胖的包子。如今出门在外，吃遍大江南北</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 28px; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">不同的早餐，北方的早</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 28px; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">餐味浓量大吃着爽，江南的早餐精致讲究花样多，但是记忆里的那碗最简单的豆浆，却是我</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 28px; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">一直牵挂的、属于我的</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 4px 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 28px; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">早餐。现在就让我们一起来细数一下中国不同地区的特色早餐，寻找属于你的家乡记忆吧！</p><div class=\"con1_info\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 24px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; height: 50px; position: relative;\"><div class=\"i1 clearfix\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; zoom: 1;\"><br /></div><span class=\"favbtns\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: block; height: 50px; width: 238px; position: absolute; right: 0px; top: 20px;\"></span><div id=\"bdshare\" class=\"bdshare_t bds_tools_32 get-codes-bdshare\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; z-index: 999999; zoom: 1; float: right !important;\"><span class=\"bds_more\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 3px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; font-family: 宋体, Arial; height: 32px; float: left; cursor: pointer; width: 37px; text-indent: -100em; background-image: url(http://bdimg.share.baidu.com/static/images/is_32.png?cdnversion=20131113) !important; background-position: 0px 5px !important; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat !important;\"></span></div></div></div></div><div class=\"custom\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); line-height: 12px;\"></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><div class=\"zt_titles1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 20px 0px 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 990px;\"></div><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: block; float: left;\"><br /></span><div class=\"r\" style=\"background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: 300px; width: 630px; float: left; position: relative;\"><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 12px 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; height: 50px; line-height: 50px; font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">北京——炒肝儿</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">老北京的早餐可就太多了，焦圈儿、豆汁儿、煎饼果子、豆腐脑儿，今</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">天给大家介绍的是其中很有“个性”的一个，炒肝儿。注意这里必须加个“儿”。北京人做人圆润开朗，说话也多带儿化音，炒肝儿并不是炒的，而是以大肠、猪肝加淀粉煮成浓浓的一碗。传统吃炒肝并不用汤匙筷子，而是整碗端起来喝。所以从前若有人吃炒肝用匙筷，老北京人一看就知道此人必为外地人</span></h3></div><br /><br /><br /><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><br /></span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><br /></span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><br /></span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><br /></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><br /></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><br /></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><br /></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><br /></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><br /></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><br /></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><br /></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><br /></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><br /></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">河南——胡辣汤</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">胡辣汤，又名糊辣汤，是中国北方早餐中常见的汤类食品。常见于街上</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">的早</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">点摊点，其特点是微</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">辣，营养丰富，味道上口，十分适合配合其它早点进餐。胡辣汤起源于河</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">南周</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">口市西华县逍遥镇的“逍遥</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">镇胡辣汤”，是一种汤</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">类小吃。由三十余种天然中草药按比例配制的汤</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">料在加入</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">胡椒和辣椒又用骨头汤做</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">底料的胡辣汤又香又辣。目前，已经发展成</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">为每个河南人都喜爱和</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">知晓的小</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">吃之一。</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><br /></span></span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">东北——疙瘩&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">这个可是正宗东北佳肴。这个早中晚都可以吃。就是把面揪成一块一块的</span></span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">扔到锅</span></span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">里做成汤，可以加白菜、菠菜、紫菜、香菜、洋柿子（西红柿）……反正就看个人喜好。有</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">人喜欢大粒疙</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">瘩，有人喜欢小粒的。也是咸的。</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><br /></span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">山东——焖子</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 28px; background-color: transparent;\">相传一百多年前，有门氏两兄弟来烟台晒粉条，有一次刚将粉胚做好，遇上</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 28px; background-color: transparent;\">了连阴</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">天，粉条晒不成，粉胚就要酸坏。情急之下，门氏兄弟将乡亲们请来用油煎粉胚，加蒜拌着吃，</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">大家异口同</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">声说好吃，有风味。于是便帮门氏兄弟支锅立灶煎粉胚卖，人们都说好吃，但问此食品叫</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">什么名，谁也说不</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">出。其中一智者认为此品是门氏兄弟所创，又用油煎焖，就脱口而出叫“焖子”。</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 50px; font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><br /></span></span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 50px; font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">天津——煎饼果子</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">介哪能妹有咱天津卫的煎饼果子，锅巴菜，鸡蛋灌儿饼呢！天津市旧</span></span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 50px; font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">称</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">天津</span></span><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">卫，是</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">守护北京的重要门户，同时也是我国北方的重要海港。天津人注重传统，也豁达乐观。</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">来一套煎饼果</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体;\">子，就着街口吃完舔舔指尖儿，融入熙熙攘攘的人群中，尝十八街麻花，园子里头听</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体;\">听戏，嘛钱不钱的，乐</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体;\">呵乐呵得了~</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><br /></span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">湖北——武汉热干面</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">热干面是武汉市颇具特色的早餐小吃。热干面原本是武汉地食品</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">，在湖北</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">很多地方(如随州、襄阳等)都十分受欢迎，热干面在黄石地区早餐也俗称凉面。随着湖北</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">人在其他省市地人口</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">增多，武汉热干面也在许多地方都能见到，是诸多人喜欢的面食之一。</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><br /></span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">江苏——灌汤包</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">灌汤包子有了形式美，其内容精美别致，肉馅与鲜汤同居一室，吃之，</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">便就将北国</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">吃面、吃肉、吃汤三位一体化，是一种整合的魅力。 吃灌汤包子，汤的存在列第一位，</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">肉馅次之，面皮次次之。</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><br /></span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">上海——上海大馄饨</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">馄饨的形状很多，有元宝状的，圆形，三角形，长方形，圆</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">筒形或者半圆形。</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">白水煮沸后入馄饨，因为馄饨皮薄所以我加一次冷水再沸腾，就出锅。馄饨汤</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">很简单，如果有猪油最上心，我只</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">是放了鸡精，盐，黑胡椒粉，紫菜还有芝麻油，另外煮开壶热</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">水，倒入即成汤。放点儿虾米。</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><br /></span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">台湾——蚵仔面线</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">说到台湾早餐，就不得不提美食南霸天台南，要说全台湾最重视早餐</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">的地方，莫过</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">于这里了。北部的传统早餐大概就是烧饼油条，但要说道南部的传统早餐，碗粿、肉粽、</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">肉燥油麵、铁板麵、担仔</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">麵、润饼捲、各式咸粥、肉包菜包、肉羹、蚵仔麵线、抓饼、葱烧饼、烧饼</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">油条、咸豆浆、水煎包、割包、素食油</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">麵、锅贴水饺蒸饺、米糕、饭糰、韭菜盒、馒头夹蛋、油饭滷</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">肉饭……信手拈来便是一长串，每天选一种不一样的</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">早餐，连续吃上一个月都没问题。</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><br /></span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">福建——沙茶面</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">厦门是个较早对外开放的城市，人们的生活中有很多舶来品，沙茶就是</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">一种。沙茶始源</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">于印尼，也有来自马来西亚一说。沙茶面的做法很简单，面条放入笊篱下开水锅烫熟</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">，捞到碗里，随自己的口味加入</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">猪肝、猪腰、鸭腱、大肠、鲜鱿鱼、豆腐干等辅料，最后淋上一直在</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">大锅里滚开的汤料，一分钟之内一碗面就可上桌了。</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><br /></span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">浙江——生煎包</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">软的小包子带着一层香香脆脆的底边，外加小葱的香气，这种复合的口感</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">总是很让人迷恋。</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">”隆冬时节，吃上刚出锅的生煎包，更有利于驱走寒气，嚼出香味，吸收营养。</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><br /></span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">广东——肠粉</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">肠粉又叫布拉蒸肠粉，是一种米制品，亦称布拉肠、拉粉、卷粉、猪肠粉(因</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">形似猪肠) ，因为早</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">市销量大，多数店家又供不应求，人们常常是排队候吃，因此又被戏称为“抢粉”。</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">出品时以“白如雪，薄如纸，油光闪亮，</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">香滑可口”著称。 在广东，肠粉是一种非常普遍的街坊美食，</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">它价廉、美味，老少咸宜，妇孺皆知，从不起眼的食肆茶市</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">，到五星级的高级酒店，几乎都有供应。</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><br /></span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">广西——桂林米粉</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">把烫热的米粉滤干，再配以锅烧(炸酥的五花肉)、卤牛肉片、香肠、叉</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">烧等，加卤水、</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">花生油、酥黄豆，再根据个人喜好加入辣椒、蒜蓉、葱花、各类酸菜等，搅拌入味。这</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">种米粉吃起来呼呼作响，声色味俱</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">全。桂林米粉已经渗入广西人生活的方方面面，早上的街头，总能</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">看到挤满人的米粉店。</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><br /></span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">云南——米线</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">米线是云南饮食文化的一个必不可少的经典，云南人早晨起来吃碗米线，算是最</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">最享受的！米线</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">在云南也分的精细，云南米线有两种，酸浆米线和干浆米线。略去制作过程不说，酸浆</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">米线筋骨好，滑爽回甜，有大米清</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">香，为传统制法，俗称——粗米线。相对的细米线即干浆米线筋骨硬、</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">咬口、线长。而口味上就更多了，过桥米线，小锅</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">米线，大锅米线，卤米线，豆花米线，凉米线，罐罐</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">米线。当然就早餐来说，一碗小锅米线，总是大家的不二选择。</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><br /></span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">重庆——酸辣粉</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">酸辣粉源于四川民间，取食材至当地手工制作的红薯粉，味以突出酸辣</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">为主而得名，后来经过</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">不断的演变和调制而正式走上街头，成为重庆的一种特色小吃。滑溜的红薯粉浸</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">泡在酸香麻辣的粉汤里，吃一碗热汗淋漓，</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">立马就从半睡半醒的状态中精神起来了。</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><br /></span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">四川——抄手</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">红油抄手乃是四川著名小吃。此种小吃柔嫩鲜美，汤汁微辣浓香。抄手是</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">四川人对馄饨的称呼，</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">馄饨在全国各地均有制作，红油抄手是最为著名的品种之一。只见包馄饨的</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">小姑娘端坐面皮与肉馅间，十指如飞，馄饨</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">如蝴蝶一只只，扑进那簸箕盘子里。不仅好吃，而且好看。</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><br /></span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">新疆——烤馕</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">“胡麻饼样学京都，面脆油香出新炉。寄予饥馋杨大使，尝看得以辅兴无。”白居</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">易诗中的胡麻饼</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">就是新疆维族人民日常生活必不可少的食材之一：馕。在面粉中加少许盐水和酵面，</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">和匀，揉透，稍发，即可烤制。添</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">加羊油的即为油馕；用羊肉丁、孜然粉、胡椒粉、洋葱末等作料拌</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">馅烤制的为肉馕；将芝麻与葡萄汁拌和烤制的叫芝麻</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">馕……种类繁多，既美味又具有民族特色。</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><br /></span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">甘肃——兰州牛肉面</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">终于轮到大名鼎鼎的兰州牛肉面了。兰州清汤牛肉拉面，兰州</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">著名风味小吃，传说起</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">源于唐代，它以“汤镜者清，肉烂者香，面细者精”的独特风味和“一清二白三</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">红四绿”的悦目色彩赢得了国内乃至全世界顾</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">客的好评，被中国烹饪协会评为三大中式快餐之一。冬</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">天的早上来一碗热气腾腾的兰州牛肉面，连汤都喝干净，从胃里</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">涌出的温暖一下子驱走严寒。</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><br /></span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft Yahei\', 黑体; font-size: 24px; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">陕西——肉夹馍</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">肉夹馍，实际是两种食物的绝妙组合：腊汁肉，白吉馍。肉夹馍合腊汁肉、</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">白吉馍为一体，</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">互为烘托，将各自滋味发挥到极致。馍香肉酥，肥而不腻，回味无穷。肉夹馍来自陕西，</span></div><div class=\"zt_con2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); width: 990px; line-height: 12px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">却能风靡我国的大江南北，在</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\">每个城市早起出门的你几乎都能发现它的影子，成了真正的国民早餐。</span></div>', '', '', '1385568614', '159', '1', '', '', '', '1', '周边小编', '1'), ('32', '10分钟教你学会做烘培', '', '<center style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"玛格丽特饼干的做法\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20110920/199e008987ab6f2c291d041ce862423b.jpg\" width=\"328\" height=\"440\" original=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20110920/199e008987ab6f2c291d041ce862423b.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\" /><br /></center><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">&nbsp; 一、玛格丽特饼干</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　原料：低筋面粉100克，玉米淀粉100克，无盐黄油100克，糖粉40克，熟蛋黄2个，盐1克。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　1.黄油室温软化，鸡蛋煮熟备用。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　2.软化的黄油+糖粉用打蛋器打发。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　3.把煮熟的鸡蛋剥掉外壳，小心取出蛋黄。蛋黄放入小筛网中用勺子碾碎，筛出细碎的蛋黄屑。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　4.玉米淀粉和低筋面粉混合过筛，与打发的黄油一起拌至无干粉。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　5.用手捏成面团放入保险单中，按瘪放入冰箱冷藏1小时左右。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　6.从冰箱取出冷藏好的面团，10克/个搓成小圆球，排入烤盘中，用食指按出小坑。烤箱预热170度，放入中层，烘焙约15分钟即可。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　</p><center style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"蔓越莓饼干的做法\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130917/50eef7f2e0e4cf637be2de35cb44d31f.jpg\" width=\"328\" height=\"440\" original=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130917/50eef7f2e0e4cf637be2de35cb44d31f.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: inline;\" /><br /></center><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">二、蔓越莓饼干</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　原料：低粉115克、蔓越莓干35克、砂糖60克、黄油75克、全蛋液15ML。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　1.原料备用，蔓越莓干切碎</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　2.黄油软化后，加入细砂糖 ，搅拌均匀，加入鸡蛋液，搅拌均匀</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　3.倒入蔓越莓干，倒入低筋面粉，搅拌均匀，成为面团</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　4.把面团倒手保鲜袋内，整形成宽约6厘米，高约4厘米的长方体</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　5.入冰箱冷冻一小时左右，切成厚0.7厘米的片，均匀的摆在铺了锡纸的烤盘内</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　6.烤箱预热170度，烤20分钟左右，表面成微黄即可</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　</p><center style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"芒果蛋挞的做法\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130821/fcc7bc5bac0f632ef2106ae5c0d642e9.jpg\" width=\"328\" height=\"440\" original=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130821/fcc7bc5bac0f632ef2106ae5c0d642e9.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: inline;\" /><br /></center><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">三、芒果蛋挞</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　原料：挞皮数个、安佳淡奶油75克 、纯牛奶70克 、炼乳7克 、绵白糖30克 、蛋黄2个、低筋粉7克 、 芒果数个。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　1.准备挞皮、淡奶油、纯牛奶 、炼乳 、绵白糖 、鸡蛋黄、低筋面粉、 芒果备用，芒果洗净，从中间切开</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　2.用刀在果肉上，划十字刀，然后用手推起，用刀取下果肉，放入冷冻蛋挞皮内</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　3.果肉平均的放入所有的挞皮内，淡奶油、牛奶、绵白糖、炼乳倒入金属容器内</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　4.一边加热，一边搅拌，至糖完全融化，放凉的挞水，放入两个蛋黄</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　5.筛入低筋面粉，搅拌均匀</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　6.挞水过筛，倒入挞皮内，8-9分满，烤箱预热220度，20分钟，倒数第二层烤好即可</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　</p><center style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"面包布丁的做法\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130705/c2860c3d726ae59dafb48d5180c702a7.jpg\" width=\"328\" height=\"440\" original=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130705/c2860c3d726ae59dafb48d5180c702a7.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: inline;\" /><br /></center><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">四、面包布丁</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　原料：吐司2片、淡奶油100克、牛奶100克、鸡蛋2个、糖25克、杏仁片</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　1.牛奶和淡奶油混合</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　2.加入白糖，微波30秒左右再搅拌一下，确保糖融化，不行可再微波10秒左右</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　3.吐司撕成丁放入烤碗中，鸡蛋2个打散成蛋液</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　4.将鸡蛋液倒入牛奶混合液中，搅拌均匀，将混合液过筛</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　5.过筛后的混合液倒入烤碗中，撒上杏仁片</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　6.入预热180的烤箱，烤20分钟左右，至表面金黄即可</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　</p><center style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"家庭版小桃酥的做法\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20120305/cb29a6c35bc4c468a0d891d8c733086c.jpg\" width=\"328\" height=\"440\" original=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20120305/cb29a6c35bc4c468a0d891d8c733086c.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: inline;\" /><br /></center><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">五、家庭版小桃酥</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　原料：标准粉100克，白砂糖50克，玉米油50克(植物油均可)，鸡蛋10克蛋清，其余蛋黄备用。熟核桃碎55克，泡打粉1/4小勺，小苏打1/8小勺</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　1.用玉米油加入打散的鸡蛋液、白砂糖在盆中混合均匀</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　2.面粉和泡打粉、小苏打混合均匀，过筛直接到搅拌好的鸡蛋液</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　3.将核桃碎倒入面粉中，混合均匀</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　4.把面粉倒入第一步的玉米油混合物，揉成面团</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　5.取一小块面团，搓成小圆球压扁。锅底点上隔热板上面铺上锡纸放上压扁的小饼，用最小火烘烤5分钟</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　6.放入烤盘前在表面刷一层蛋黄液，放入预热好的烤箱中层，180度，12分钟左右，烤到表面金黄色即可</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　</p><center style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"黄油曲奇的做法\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130911/11ea0017a825b1f57e4e42ae931294a4.jpg\" width=\"328\" height=\"440\" original=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130911/11ea0017a825b1f57e4e42ae931294a4.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: inline;\" /><br /></center><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">六、黄油曲奇</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　原料：黄油100g，糖粉40g，金像高粉100g，玉米淀粉50g，全蛋液30g</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　1.黄油室温充分软化成膏状</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　2.加入糖粉打发到颜色变浅，呈羽毛状</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　3.蛋液充分打散变浅，分三次加入，每次加入后用刮刀按压至全部吸收后再加入剩下的蛋液</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　4.蛋液全部拌入后的状态</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　5.筛入混合均匀的高筋面粉与淀粉</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　6.刮刀按压均匀，不颗粒</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　7.将太阳花裱花嘴装入裱花袋，放入曲奇面糊</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　8.挤入不沾烤盘，如果用普通烤盘请垫油纸。烤箱预热200度，烤约15分钟左右</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　</p><center style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"面包披萨的做法\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20120309/19e697ac269fc6d1248aa79d123fa933.jpg\" width=\"328\" height=\"440\" original=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20120309/19e697ac269fc6d1248aa79d123fa933.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: inline;\" /><br /></center><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">七、面包披萨</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　原料：全麦面包、马苏里拉奶酪、鲜虾、蔬菜粒、番茄沙司</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　1.鲜虾去皮去虾线洗净控干待用，将蔬菜类用开水焯一下</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　2.面包上挤上番茄沙司</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　3.放上鲜虾(为了省时鲜嫩也可以将虾用微波炉略打30秒)</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　4.放上蔬菜粒，马苏里拉奶酪丝(也可以选择切达奶酪，但是不拉丝)</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　5.烤箱预热200度，烤10分钟奶酪融化即可</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　</p><center style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"柠檬芝士小蛋糕的做法\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131128/b5fedb43381faef1d9e04b44d4a4008f.jpg\" width=\"328\" height=\"440\" original=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131128/b5fedb43381faef1d9e04b44d4a4008f.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: inline;\" /><br /></center><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">八、柠檬芝士小蛋糕</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　原料：芝士200克,糖165克,鸡蛋4枚,柠檬皮屑1只,低筋面粉185克。份量：中号纸杯12个。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　1.芝士隔热水用打蛋器搅打顺滑</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　2.加入白糖搅拌均匀</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　3.分次加入鸡蛋搅打均匀</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　4.加入柠檬皮屑拌匀</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　5.筛入低筋面粉用刮刀拌匀</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　6.舀入纸杯，轻轻磕几下让气泡排除。烤箱预热180度，中层上下火约30分钟</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　</p><center style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"奶油奶酪布丁的做法\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131101/2abaf1b0fb51d05f3ef088057fd6e0a8.jpg\" width=\"328\" height=\"440\" original=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131101/2abaf1b0fb51d05f3ef088057fd6e0a8.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: inline;\" /><br /></center><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">九、奶油奶酪布丁</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　原料：奶酪奶酪40g，幼砂糖30g，牛奶140g，淡奶油100g，鸡蛋1个，柠檬汁2.5g</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　1.奶油奶酪及牛奶放入容器中，隔热水用打蛋器慢慢搅打，至奶油奶酪与牛奶混合均匀，无颗粒</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　2.倒入淡奶油，搅拌均匀</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　3.全蛋磕入碗中，用筷子打散</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　4.将奶油奶酪液体分多次加入蛋液中，并轻轻搅拌，混合均匀后，过筛，得到细腻的布丁液</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　5.将过筛后的布丁液倒入奶瓶中，将奶瓶放入盛器中，倒入凉水</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　6.入150℃预热的烤箱，中层，水浴法烤30~40分钟，取出放凉后冷藏一夜食用</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　</p><center style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"酸奶油杯子蛋糕的做法\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130521/75a0f1c7e1446a93782511f18f6b7565.jpg\" width=\"328\" height=\"440\" original=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130521/75a0f1c7e1446a93782511f18f6b7565.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: inline;\" /><br /></center><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">十、酸奶油杯子蛋糕</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　蛋糕：1/4杯黄油，1/2杯白 糖，1个鸡蛋，1杯酸奶油，1杯低粉，1/2茶匙泡打粉，少许苏打粉，1/2茶匙香草精</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　内馅：1/8杯黄糖，1/4杯低粉，1 1/2茶匙黄油，1/2杯核桃碎</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　1.黄油加糖打发，加入鸡蛋，搅匀;加入酸奶油，香草精，搅匀;加入过筛的粉类</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　2.搅加入的粉类拌均匀，将内馅材料一起加入碗中搅匀;先放一半的蛋糕糊放入纸膜中</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　3.然后加入一小勺内馅，然后再加入蛋糕糊;在地上用地敲平蛋糕糊，入烤箱350华氏，25分钟即可</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">看到这里，还没买烤箱的童鞋是不是有点沮丧，莫着急，洒家准备了几个味道超赞且不需要烤箱，只要有平底锅就能搞定的糕点美味，走起~~</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　</p><center style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"枣香南瓜发糕的做法\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131107/a41769e8d457c574f651c4d36c73d576.jpg\" width=\"328\" height=\"440\" original=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131107/a41769e8d457c574f651c4d36c73d576.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: inline;\" /><br /></center><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">枣香南瓜发糕</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　原料：蒸熟的南瓜 175g , 普通面粉300g , 奶粉25g, 牛奶96 g, 白糖40 g, 发酵粉4g，红枣粒50g</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　1.南瓜去皮切块后隔水蒸熟</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　2. 用滤网滤成细腻的南瓜泥</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　3.所有的材料一起放在一个大盆中，发酵粉和白糖要分隔开来</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　4.用拌勺拌起成面团状</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　5.红枣洗净去核后切成小粒加一半到面团中，翻拌均匀</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　6. 将格拉斯内壁上抹一层黄油防粘，将拌好的面团放入表面抹平(放1/2满)</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　7. 表面撒上另一半红枣粒放入蒸锅中醒发</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　8.发酵至2倍大时，大火烧开后转中火蒸25-30分钟，关火后焖5分钟取出</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　</p><center style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"弥猴桃班戟的做法\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131121/ebd39878cbfa897c2477da3559d769d7.jpg\" width=\"328\" height=\"440\" original=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131121/ebd39878cbfa897c2477da3559d769d7.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: inline;\" /><br /></center><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">弥猴桃班戟</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　饼皮配方：鸡蛋黄2个，细砂糖150克，牛奶110克，黄油7克，低筋面粉50克</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　内馅配方：淡奶油100克，细砂糖20克，水果适量</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　以上可做4个。这里配方不用太严格，饼皮糊调成较稀可流动的就行，跟我们平时摊鸡蛋饼差不多，只用蛋黄是为了颜色漂亮，如果不在意可用一个全蛋代替。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　1.蛋黄加入细砂糖，搅拌均匀，加入牛奶拌匀</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　2.加入过筛后的面粉拌匀，静置15分钟后加入溶化的黄油拌匀</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　3.过筛成为细腻的蛋糊</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　4.炒锅锅底抹薄薄一层油，烧热转小火，加入一勺蛋糊，至蛋皮鼓起大泡即可</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　5.淡奶油加入细砂糖，打至全发</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　6.饼皮放凉后，取一张，底面朝上，在中心铺一块淡奶油，放半颗猕猴桃，再铺上淡奶油，上下左右包起来即可</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　</p><center style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"鲜虾三明治的做法\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130912/eceb888d1af9effb6bf18f05c2d0d60b.jpg\" width=\"328\" height=\"440\" original=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20130912/eceb888d1af9effb6bf18f05c2d0d60b.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: inline;\" /><br /></center><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">鲜虾三明治</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　原料：面包片3片，虾10只，黄瓜半根，西红柿半个，鸡蛋2个，面粉1/4杯，沙拉酱适量</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　1.虾10只左右，去掉头和皮，还有虾线，然后放入开水锅中煮熟，捞出后将虾剖开，让它变得薄一点</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　2.黄瓜和西红柿切片</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　3.再调一碗鸡蛋面糊，两颗蛋+1汤匙面粉，调成细细的糊状</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　4.料备齐后就可以做三明治了，先在面包上涂上一层沙拉酱，摆上几片番茄</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　5.再放几片黄瓜，最后是一层虾仁，再盖上一片涂好沙拉酱的面包</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　6.第一层完成，按照刚才的顺序再盖一层，然后把四个边切掉</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　7.最后裹上一层蛋汁，放入油锅中炸成金黄色，取出切块就好了</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">看完了不收走，就枉费了洒家一片苦心呐<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; line-height: 21px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">︽⊙＿⊙︽</span></span></span></p>', '', '', '1385829112', '226', '1', '', '', '', '1', '周边小编', '1');
INSERT INTO `articles` VALUES ('33', '做鱼也可以如此的简单', '', '<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 鱼类含有丰富的蛋白质，而且味道鲜美，易于消化，非常适合老人和孩子吃。但是说起吃鱼，大家都会很头疼，看着滑溜溜的，无从下手，总觉的还不如炒点肉来的实在，也简单。其实做鱼真的很简单，一道清蒸鱼也就10来分钟的时间，而且还不油不腻，干炸、红烧、水煮或者炖汤，也都很简单，10种做法让你吃个够。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><strong>一、清蒸鲈鱼</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><img class=\"conimg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131119/a3b07932178945e6a51b6a55ea0b7b71.jpg\" alt=\"清蒸鲈鱼.jpg\" width=\"328\" height=\"440\" original=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131119/a3b07932178945e6a51b6a55ea0b7b71.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: block; max-width: 550px;\" /></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">用料：鲈鱼1条、食盐3克、姜5克、蒜5克、料酒适量、青蒜30克、猪油(炼)1勺、蒸鱼豉油30克</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">1、材料：鲈鱼、青蒜、姜、猪油和蒸鱼豉油</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">2、鲈鱼处理好后洗净，用厨房纸擦干，两面分别划几刀，并用少许盐抹遍鱼身的内外，腌制10分钟以上(盐宜少不宜多，最后要浇蒸鱼豉油)</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">3、鱼肚内塞上姜和蒜，鱼身也撒上姜蒜，并倒上少许料酒，大火烧开后入锅蒸10分钟左右，关火后再虚蒸5分钟</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">4、蒸好的鱼，去除姜和蒜，并把盘内的汤汁倒掉(这步很重要，鱼的腥味都是在这汤汁里了，倒掉鱼就没那么腥了)</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">5、鱼身重新撒上姜蒜丝，浇上一勺烧热的猪油(可以用色拉油，但猪油会更香，一定要浇在姜蒜丝上，这样姜蒜和鱼的香味才能充分激发)</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">6、上桌前再浇上蒸鱼豉油，清蒸鲈鱼就做好了</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><strong>二、剁椒鱼头</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><img class=\"conimg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131119/1f5b688e9b5622767c4cf53c02dde81a.jpg\" alt=\"剁椒鱼头.jpg\" width=\"328\" height=\"440\" original=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131119/1f5b688e9b5622767c4cf53c02dde81a.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: block; max-width: 550px;\" /></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">用料：鱼头1个、剁椒1把、葱半棵、姜2小块、食盐1茶匙、植物油1汤匙、料酒适量、水淀粉少许</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">1、鱼头洗净切半，用刀在鱼肉上划两刀，以便更入味</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">2、用1茶匙盐均匀的抹上鱼头上，上下铺上姜丝，淋上料酒和植物油腌制10分钟左右</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">3、鱼头铺上适量的剁椒，不爱吃辣的可以少放些</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">4、水烧开后，入锅蒸12分钟，再虚蒸3分钟至熟</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">5、蒸鱼会有多出的汤汁，把汤汁回锅烧</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">6、加少许水淀粉勾芡一下稍加收收干再淋回鱼头上</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">7、再淋上少许葱油增香(葱白放油锅中炸香，即成葱油)</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">8、放上葱丝即可上桌</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><strong>三、鲫鱼豆腐汤</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><img class=\"conimg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131119/0b89c4ae02e672bca1aca42b92b2a32a.jpg\" alt=\"鲫鱼豆腐汤.jpg\" width=\"328\" height=\"440\" original=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131119/0b89c4ae02e672bca1aca42b92b2a32a.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: block; max-width: 550px;\" /></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">用料：鲫鱼1条、豆腐350克、真姬菇150克、料酒15克、食盐3克、姜5片、葱白5段、香菜2根、白胡椒粉3克、花生油50克、水1.5升</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">1、鲫鱼让鱼档工作人员帮忙开膛去除内脏、鳞、腮，回家后洗净去除鲫鱼腹内的黑膜，然后抹干，用盐和料酒腌制去腥</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">2、豆腐切成块，白玉菇(真姬菇)摘净用盐水浸泡15分钟后控水备用</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">3、老姜切片，葱白切段，香菜洗净切断</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">4、提前用姜片擦一下炒锅防粘，开火将锅烧热后放入适量花生油，下鲫鱼煎至两面金黄，加入葱姜</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">5、倒入约1-1.5升的开水，盖上锅盖大火烧开后继续大火煲10分钟至汤色奶白后转小火煲30分钟</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">6、30分钟后加入豆腐、白玉菇中小火煲10-15分钟</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">7、出锅前5分钟，调入1勺盐、1勺白胡椒粉</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">8、出锅后按喜好撒上香菜即可食用</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><strong>四、干炸小黄鱼</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><img class=\"conimg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131119/38a73643562fad75b9c3e84ce32b88a7.jpg\" alt=\"干炸小黄鱼.jpg\" width=\"328\" height=\"440\" original=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131119/38a73643562fad75b9c3e84ce32b88a7.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: block; max-width: 550px;\" /></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">用料：小黄花鱼500克、淀粉25克、小麦面粉100克、料酒2汤匙、小葱2根、姜1片、食盐1茶匙、植物油适量、黑胡椒粉少许</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">1、小黄鱼去鳞、去鳃(也可去鱼头)、去内脏后洗净备用</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">2、取大碗一只，将小黄鱼用料酒、葱段、姜丝和盐，抓匀腌30分钟左右</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">3、取一个大盘子，撒上面粉与淀粉，将腌好后的小黄鱼放入盘子中</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">4、逐个均匀包裹上干面粉待用，油热放入小黄鱼，小火慢炸</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">5、捞出放一会儿再放入油锅复炸一遍，这样小黄鱼更酥，小黄鱼出锅后，可以撒上一些黑胡椒粉，味道更棒</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><strong>五、红烧鲫鱼</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><img class=\"conimg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131119/b074c904c63acfa7bdb20459d7b7b2a7.jpg\" alt=\"红烧鲫鱼.jpg\" width=\"328\" height=\"440\" original=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131119/b074c904c63acfa7bdb20459d7b7b2a7.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: block; max-width: 550px;\" /></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">用料：鲫鱼1条、酱油5克、料酒5克、细香葱5克、鸡精3克、食盐5克、白糖3克、植物油20克、葱5克、姜3片、蒜3瓣</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">1、 炒锅烧热倒植物油，下入葱姜蒜爆出香味，下入鱼煎至两面金黄，淋入适量料酒和酱油、盐</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">2、冲入适量开水持平鱼身，开大火将汤汁收干，江浙口味的话可以适当的撒点白砂糖进去，出锅前撒入适量鸡精和细香葱花即可</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><strong>六、超美味酸菜鱼</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><img class=\"conimg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131119/281a0d3547505e158f44715941412a7c.jpg\" alt=\"超美味酸菜鱼.jpg\" width=\"328\" height=\"440\" original=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131119/281a0d3547505e158f44715941412a7c.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: block; max-width: 550px;\" /></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">用料：鲤鱼1条、酸菜半颗、鸡蛋清20克、葱1根、姜1块、干辣椒1小把、水适量、色拉油适量、野山椒5克、蒜5克、食盐3克、淀粉2小勺、白酒几滴、八角2个、花椒20粒、胡椒粉2克</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">1、鲤鱼肚子里的内脏去掉，鱼鳞刮干净，剪去鱼鳍并冲洗多次后，去除腥线</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">2、沿着鱼的主刺用刀将鱼一片为二，将鱼肉片成大小适中的鱼片，鱼头剁两半，鱼骨剁小块</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">3、在鱼片里加入适量盐，打入半个蛋清，2小勺淀粉、几滴白酒、少许胡椒粉拌匀，腌制半个小时左右，鱼头、鱼尾、鱼骨也加少许盐和胡椒粉腌制</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">4、葱切碎、姜切丝、辣椒用剪刀剪开去掉籽，酸菜事先浸泡2小时，然后切丝入热水锅焯几分钟，然后捞出沥干水分</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">5、锅里放1勺油，开小火，凉油下锅一半的辣椒,加入葱姜蒜、八角、花椒和野山椒煸炒，下入切丝的酸菜翻炒，将鱼头、鱼骨和鱼尾放入锅中翻炒，翻炒均匀后倒入热水，水中加入适量盐</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">6、等水沸腾后转中火炖5分钟，将腌好的鱼片一片片丢入水中，鱼片一熟就关火，将酸菜、汤和鱼一同倒入一个盆中</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">7、1大勺油倒入锅中，小火加热，油七成热后关火，将剩下的干红辣椒段放入油里，并迅速浇在盆里的鱼肉上，酸菜鱼即成</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><strong>七、麻辣水煮鱼</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><img class=\"conimg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131119/2073677bd9ec7b1b60bc466f7a4d5106.jpg\" alt=\"麻辣水煮鱼.jpg\" width=\"328\" height=\"440\" original=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131119/2073677bd9ec7b1b60bc466f7a4d5106.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: block; max-width: 550px;\" /></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">用料：龙利鱼500克、鸡蛋清1个、黄豆芽500克、花椒1小把、干辣椒30个、郫县豆瓣酱1大匙、葱10克、姜5克、蒜5克、食盐3克、料酒5克、淀粉5克、植物油适量</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">1、首先将原料和调料都准备就绪，豆芽洗净，葱段、姜片、蒜片都切好，干红辣椒用厨房纸巾擦干净</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">2、鱼肉切成片，加一个蛋清，少许盐、料酒、淀粉浆上</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">3、黄豆芽入沸水锅中焯至断生，焯的时候加适量盐</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">4、将焯好的黄豆芽平铺在盆子底部</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">5、锅内放适量油，加入花椒粒小火炸出香味</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">6、关火后再放入干红辣椒稍炸后一并捞出备用</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">7、放入一大匙剁碎的郫县豆瓣酱炒出红油</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">8、加入姜片和蒜片同炒片刻</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">9、加入适量热水烧开，水量以大约没过鱼片为宜</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">10、将鱼片逐片下入锅中，煮至鱼片变成白色之后，连同汤一起倒入放黄豆芽的盆中</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">11、把先前炸过的花椒粒和干红辣椒、葱段一起放在上面</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">12、另取一锅放适量油烧热，淋入盆中即可</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><strong>八、红烧带鱼</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><img class=\"conimg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131119/9eae3e678130c64d9083d6fbe422f720.jpg\" alt=\"红烧带鱼.jpg\" width=\"328\" height=\"440\" original=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131119/9eae3e678130c64d9083d6fbe422f720.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: block; max-width: 550px;\" /></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">用料：带鱼1条、红椒1/2个、小葱1棵、姜1块、蒜4瓣、料酒2汤匙、生抽2汤匙、老抽2汤匙、白糖1茶匙、食盐1/2茶匙、淀粉2汤匙、植物油3汤匙、水适量</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">1、带鱼处理干净、切段，加入1/2茶匙盐</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">2、再加入2汤匙料酒，腌制15分钟，红椒切段、葱切段、姜切末、蒜切片</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">3、锅中烧植物油至七成热，带鱼段擦干水分、拍淀粉，放入锅中煎至两面金黄，盛出沥干油分</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">4、锅中留底油，放入葱姜蒜爆香</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">5、放入煎好的带鱼段，加入生抽和老抽</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">6、再加入少许白糖，加入适量清水没过带鱼，大火烧开后转中小火，烧至汤汁浓稠，撒上少许葱花和红椒块即可</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><strong>九、时蔬烤秋刀鱼</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><img class=\"conimg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131119/2cdef3757838ca944e64a626a64ec064.jpg\" alt=\"时蔬烤秋刀鱼.jpg\" width=\"328\" height=\"440\" original=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131119/2cdef3757838ca944e64a626a64ec064.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: block; max-width: 550px;\" /></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">用料：秋刀鱼650克、红椒1/2个、黄椒1/2个、柿子椒1/2个、食盐8克、黑胡椒粉2克、椒盐2克、孜然2克、橄榄油10克</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">1、准备材料：秋刀鱼650克、红黄绿彩椒各半个(也可以换成别的蔬菜)</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">2、盐、黑胡椒粉、椒盐和孜然粉混合均匀</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">3、彩椒洗净切块，撒少许盐拌匀腌制一会(用盐腌制一会彩椒会出水，烤的时候就不会出太多水了，也更入味)</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">4、秋刀鱼去内脏，洗净充分擦干，鱼身正反面都划斜刀，鱼身内外均匀的抹上调料，腌制半小时以上</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">5、秋刀鱼身正反面都刷上橄榄油，入预热的烤箱，200度烤20分钟后取出翻面，撒上彩椒块，再撒上剩余的调料，继续烤10分钟左右(吃的时候，可以挤些柠檬汁在上面，酸酸的和秋刀鱼很搭，不过我家人不喜欢)</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><strong>十、麻椒鲅鱼</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><img class=\"conimg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131119/31a531952255ca8f23c0183cc1d66e20.jpg\" alt=\"麻椒鲅鱼.jpg\" width=\"328\" height=\"440\" original=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131119/31a531952255ca8f23c0183cc1d66e20.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: block; max-width: 550px;\" /></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">用料：鲅鱼2条、食盐3克、料酒15克、植物油3汤匙、辣豆豉20克、麻椒10克、葱1段、蒜4瓣、姜3片、生抽15克、白糖5克</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">1、冷冻的鲅鱼先解冻至稍微有些软，不要等完全解冻，然后处理掉内脏，去头去尾，切薄片，抹一层麻椒碎，盐、料酒码入盘中，腌制30分钟</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">2、锅中热油，放入鲅鱼中小火煎至两面金黄，锅中放油，葱姜蒜放入爆香</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">3、放入辣豆豉，将鱼块放入锅中</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">4、然后加入少量热水，调入生抽和白糖，稍微晃动锅子使得均匀，不要用铲子乱翻，以免鲅鱼都碎掉，盖盖小火焖10分钟，最后收汁即可</p>', '', '', '1385915933', '187', '1', '', '', '', '1', '周边小编', '1'), ('34', '糍粑、年糕的历史来源', '', '<p style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; POSITION: relative; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 10px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 20px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 20px; FONT: 14px/24px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 10px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 糍粑，有些地方也叫年糕、粑糍。用糯米制作而成，是我国南方一些地区流行的美食，在南方许多地区，人们习惯于在春节前制作，春节期间和春节之后食用。</p><p style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; POSITION: relative; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 10px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 20px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 20px; FONT: 14px/24px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 10px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px auto; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; DISPLAY: block; MAX-WIDTH: 550px; FONT-SIZE: 14px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"conimg\" alt=\"糍粑2.jpg\" src=\"/data/upload/7j/6l/529f35e9d3241_600x480.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"300\" original=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131119/61c51d1924e8e53d57452afd76e2a29c.jpg\" /></p><p style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; POSITION: relative; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 10px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 20px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 20px; FONT: 14px/24px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 10px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 相传春秋战国时期，楚国的臣子伍子胥为报父仇投奔了吴国，想从吴国借兵讨伐楚国。他来到吴国帮助吴王阖闾坐稳了江山，成了吴国的有功之臣。不久，他实现了自己的宏愿，率领吴兵攻破了楚国京都郢都，掘楚王墓鞭尸以报仇雪恨。此后，伍子胥受封申地。有一次吴王令他率人修建了著名的“阖闾大城”，以防侵略。城建成后，吴王大喜。惟有伍子胥闷闷不乐。他自知自己结怨甚多，恐日后有人难以容他。回营后，便对自己的亲信说，“大王喜而忘忧，不会有好下场。我死后，如国家有难，百姓受饥，在相门(苏州八个城门之一)城下掘地三尺，便可找到充饥的食物也。”阖闾的儿子夫差继位后，多次拒绝伍子胥的忠告，竟听信谗言，令伍子胥自刎身亡。不出伍子胥所料，他去世后不久，越国勾践乘机举兵伐吴，将吴国都城团团围住。</p><p style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; POSITION: relative; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 10px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 20px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 20px; FONT: 14px/24px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 10px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;当时正值年关，天寒地冻，城内民众断食，饿殍遍野，国家和人民果然遭到危难。在此危难之际，人们想起了伍子胥生前的嘱咐，便暗中拆城墙挖地，人们惊奇地发现，城基都是用熟糯米压制成的砖石。原来，这是伍子胥在建城时将大批糯米蒸熟压成砖块放凉后，作为城墙的基石储备下来的备荒粮。人们不禁感叹道，伍子胥真有先见之明!大家将糯米砖石拙起，敲碎，重新蒸煮，分而食之。后来，在楚天一带，人们每到丰年年底，便要用糯米制成像当年“城砖”一样的糍粑，以此来祭奠伍子胥。</p><p style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; POSITION: relative; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 10px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 20px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 20px; FONT: 14px/24px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 10px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 至今，糍粑仍是南方各地人民每年春节前必做的美食。有的地方将糍粑制作成圆形，有大有小，象征着丰收、喜庆和团圆。有的地方又称为年糕，这一名称也是寓意吉祥如意，人们常说：“年糕，年糕，年丰寿高”。年糕以苏州观前街的稻香村年糕为最佳品。这儿有猪油年糕和果仁红、白糖年糕。做年糕所用的糯米粉细而甜，色泽白亮，制成的年糕蒸煮煎都可，吃起来又香又甜。猪油年糕又有玫瑰、桂花、枣泥等四个品种，其共同特点是色泽鲜亮，肥润香糯，久吃不厌。我国人民吃的年糕有南式、北式之分，苏州年糕是南式年糕中很受欢迎的名特产品。</p>', '', '', '1386165834', '187', '1', '', '', '', '1', '周边小编', '1'), ('35', '身体补什么熬夜才不累', '', '<p style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; POSITION: relative; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 10px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 20px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 20px; FONT: 14px/24px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 10px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 年关难度，搁在现在的社会已然不是说的揭不开锅的那点事儿了。更多的是职场的白领们，由于到了年底，公司各项工作进人冲刺阶段，任务十分繁重!紧张的工作节奏让人情绪焦虑、身体紧绷，再加上要赶进度，每天都在加班熬夜，甚至于想休息的时候却出现了失眠症状。</p><p style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; POSITION: relative; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 10px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 20px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 20px; FONT: 14px/24px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 10px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　面对这些身不由己的状况，怎么样才能尽量的减少熬夜的危害呢?首先熬夜会使人的肠胃循环变差，所以晚餐不能吃太饱，并以清淡为主，多选择蔬菜、汤粥、水果等的食物，避免吃的太过油腻、辛辣，这样对熬夜时的健康是十分有帮助的，其次对于经常熬夜的人吃什么的问题，其实最重要的还是丰富膳食的安排，多补充维生素等各种营养物质。</p><p style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; POSITION: relative; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 10px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 20px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 20px; FONT: 14px/24px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 10px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong>　　1、补充维生素A</strong></p><p style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; POSITION: relative; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 10px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 20px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 20px; FONT: 14px/24px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 10px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　熬夜时大多是在在昏暗的灯光下奋斗，这样很容易造成眼肌疲劳、视力下降等。这时候要注意，应该尽量的多吃一些含有维生素A的食物，这类食物对预防视力减弱有一定效果，并且维生素A还可以调节视网膜感光物质，从而提高熬夜工作者对昏暗光线的适应力，并且有效的防止视觉疲劳。</p><p style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; POSITION: relative; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 10px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 20px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 20px; FONT: 14px/24px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 10px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　含维生素A丰富的食物：南瓜、胡萝卜、动物肝脏、莴笋叶、菠菜、苜蓿、白菜、豌豆、西红柿、芹菜、蛋类、牛奶、豌豆苗、青椒、鱼肝油等。</p><table style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px auto; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; BORDER-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BORDER-COLLAPSE: collapse; FONT: 14px/24px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"500\" align=\"center\"><tbody style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 14px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\"><tr style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 14px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\"><td style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: center; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\"><img style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"conimg\" alt=\"熬夜三宝，夜猫子要多吃\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131202/54e255bdf0140e6eaf51a00ed9194613.jpg\" original=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131202/54e255bdf0140e6eaf51a00ed9194613.jpg\" /></td><td style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\"><img style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"conimg\" alt=\"熬夜三宝，夜猫子要多吃\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131202/4e7ef118d6c391b583ac791ff883ef0d.jpg\" original=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131202/4e7ef118d6c391b583ac791ff883ef0d.jpg\" /></td><td style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\"><img style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"conimg\" alt=\"熬夜三宝，夜猫子要多吃\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131202/9888285e4df7a036bf02ae2538df3d87.jpg\" original=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131202/9888285e4df7a036bf02ae2538df3d87.jpg\" /></td></tr><tr style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 14px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\"><td style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\"><div style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" align=\"center\">凉拌菠菜</div></td><td style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\"><div style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" align=\"center\">泡椒猪肝</div></td><td style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\"><div style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" align=\"center\">芹菜炒肉</div></td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; POSITION: relative; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 10px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 20px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 20px; FONT: 14px/24px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 10px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　<strong>　2、蛋白质</strong></p><p style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; POSITION: relative; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 10px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 20px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 20px; FONT: 14px/24px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 10px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　一般情况下都是因为完不成工作才需要加班，因此在加班的时候多半工作量都比较大，这个时候耗能也比较多，这种情况下一定要注意多补充优质蛋白。很多食物中都含有蛋白质，而动物类食物中的蛋白最为丰富同时还利于吸收，因此在日常的生活中应该多吃一些含有蛋白质的食物。</p><p style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; POSITION: relative; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 10px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 20px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 20px; FONT: 14px/24px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 10px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　含蛋白质丰富的食物：除了我们餐桌上经常食用的奶、畜肉、禽肉、蛋类、鱼、虾等动物蛋白;还要添加豆类、芝麻、瓜子、核桃、 杏仁、松子等干果类食物。</p><table style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px auto; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; BORDER-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BORDER-COLLAPSE: collapse; FONT: 14px/24px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(102,102,102); VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"500\" align=\"center\"><tbody style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 14px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\"><tr style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: none; OUTLINE-COLOR: invert; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; OUTLINE-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 14px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\"><td style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: center; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; MARGIN: 0px; OUTLINE-STYLE: