02); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">六、颠覆传统花样饺</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　吃惯了平时的饺子，来点新花样，从饺子皮、饺子馅到饺子包法来个大变身。饺子皮经常用普通面粉未免太单调，用蔬菜汁和面来给饺子增加梦幻色彩的同时，吃着也更美味。生活亦如此，偶尔改变下常规思路，或许会收获更多的惊喜。</p><table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"97%\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 24px;\"><tbody style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><td width=\"33%\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"conimg\" border=\"0\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" alt=\"末日级美味 冬至传统饺子大全\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20100418/df43fdb611e8e27eb30f3409abd015a6_150x150.jpg\" original=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20100418/df43fdb611e8e27eb30f3409abd015a6_150x150.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: inline;\" /></td><td width=\"34%\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"><img class=\"conimg\" border=\"0\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" alt=\"末日级美味 冬至传统饺子大全\" src=\"http:/