"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">梅花饺子</td><td align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">多彩饺子</td><td align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">米饭饺子</td></tr><tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\"></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">最后再来一叠饺子的蘸水，尽情享受美味吧，自己的做的实惠，放心，怎么吃都好吃~&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"><img class=\"conimg\" alt=\"无标题-2.jpg\" src=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131219/7653a39a89ebd133ba6618c8cffb2801.jpg\" border=\"0\" original=\"http://images.meishij.net/p/20131219/7653a39a89ebd133ba6618c8cffb2801.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; display: block; max-width: 550px;\" /></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　1.蒜拍碎，捣成泥；新鲜蒜苗洗净，先切丝儿，再横刀切成小丁；另备香菜几根，蚝油</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　2.把捣好的蒜泥放碗里，再加辣椒面，多少随你口味，白芝麻少许，提香</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　3.起油滑锅，烧7成热，加花椒粒炒出香味，稍凉泼入蒜蓉辣椒面里，撒香菜碎和蒜苗碎，拌匀</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\">　　4.吃的时候，加入生抽、蚝油(少量)和醋，再加适量凉开水和盐、鸡精，搅拌均匀就可以蘸饺子吃了</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"><br /></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); position: relative;\"></p><p class=\"content\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(97, 97, 97); line-height: 1.5; font-family: arial; background-color: rgb(248, 241, 241);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-color: rgb(250, 239, 240);\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"> &nbsp; 周边网</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 